column7: How do you encourage Baby to start crawling?
column8:
You let Baby have a ball chasing and crawling after this exciting toy! Nemo “swims” as the ball moves along, while the beads inside roll around and rattle. All the movement and sounds catch your little one’s attention, getting Baby to move, too! By getting the ball to roll, your child is also learning about cause and effect. And the bright colors and beads help stimulate Baby’s senses!

Features
• Nemo “swims” as the ball rolls, encouraging Baby to crawl and chase along
• Beads inside the ball roll around and rattle for even more stimulation
• Helps develop gross motor skills, introduces cause and effect, and more!

column7: Watch your little one get up and go with the Fisher-Price® Rock ’n Roll Wagon!
column8:
This action-packed wagon features two modes of play that will grow with baby. In Sit & Play mode, there are lots of busy activities to entertain baby, including a bat-at rollerball, colorful clicker steering wheel, peek-a-boo flip page and a clacker-bead flag. When baby flips down the tailgate and presses the lever, he’ll be rewarded with fun sound effects and cars that race out the back—encouraging crawl and chase fun! In Stand & Walk mode, baby will be encouraged to walk with exciting music and cars that rock back and forth on the ramps as he pulls the wagon along. Includes two Silly Speedsters™ vehicles with rollerball bottoms and rattle bead sounds.

Features
• Two modes of play grow with baby and help develop gross motor skills
• Sit & Play mode features lots of busy activities: bat-at-rollerball, spinning and clicking steering wheel, peek-a-boo flip page, and clacker-bead flag
• Stand & Walk mode encourages baby to walk with rewarding music and cars that rock back and forth as wagon is pulled long
• Flip down the tailgate and press the lever to activate great sound effects and send cars racing out the back for crawl & chase fun
• Includes two Silly Speedsters™ vehicles with rollerball bottoms and rattle bead sounds
• Requires 2 AA batteries

Gross Motor
Baby can sit & play with vehicles and busy activities, or press the lever to send vehicles racing out the back for crawl & chase fun, or stand & pull the wagon along!

Thinking & Problem Solving
Figuring out how to make things happen helps baby develop problem solving skills! Music plays as baby pulls the wagon along, and the cars rock ’n roll back & forth on the ramps!

Sensory
Exciting music, rattling rollerball sounds and bright colors help stimulate baby’s senses.



This product is sold exclusively at Toys R Us.

Laugh & Learn® Smart Stages™ Tea Cart Walker
column7: Time to share a pot of tea—with two cups, tasty treats and plenty of songs, sounds and fun phrases!
column8:
Push the tea cart along to help steady first steps and to hear rewarding songs and musical tunes. When baby twists the tea pot, phrases and sounds bring it to life. Pressing three colorful shapes introduces colors and shapes. While baby is busy hearing about manners and sharing, she can toggle the teacups or slide the cupcake for early role play fun.

The Tea Cart Walker includes Smart Stages™ technology, an exciting new way to change learning content as baby grows. Every baby develops at their own pace, and Smart Stages™ gives you the ability to select the stage that’s best for your child! There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play – just slide the switch!

Smart Stages™ Technology
Level 1 – Explore – 9M+
First words and sounds spark baby’s curiosity
Level 2 - Encourage – 12M+
Prompt baby though questions and simple directions
Level 3 – Pretend – 18M+
Imaginative fun and early role play

Features
• 50+ pretty sing-along songs, tunes & phrases
• Includes Smart Stages™ technology – learning content changes as baby grows
• Three levels of play offer fresh songs, phrases & sounds for your little one’s age & stage
• Manual switch for Smart Stages™ level changes
• Sturdy tea cart helps steady first steps
• Push the tea cart along to hear rewarding musical tunes & songs
• Three light-up shapes to press
• Twist the teapot for phrases & sounds
• Pretty in pink tea theme helps inspire early role play
• Two toggle teacups & a cupcake slider
• No cords, no plugs, no hassle
• Introduces early academics like sharing, manners, colors, shapes & more
• Requires 3 AA batteries

There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play – just slide the switch!

Smart Stages™ Technology
Level 1 – Explore – 6M+
First words and sounds spark baby’s curiosity
Level 2 - Encourage – 12M+
Prompt baby though questions and simple directions
Level 3 – Pretend – 18M+
Imaginative fun and early role play

column7: Thomas & Friends™ Preschool Shape Sorter Toy for Toddlers
column8:
Full steam ahead for a Thomas & Friends™ twist on the classic shape sorter toy! Designed to look like Tidmouth Sheds from Thomas & Friends™, this beneficial playtime staple combines a tried-and-true preschool play pattern with the fun-filled world of Thomas. Place the provided shapes into the corresponding openings on the roof of Tidmouth Sheds, and when the star is pressed into the appropriate recess, Thomas will roll out from the center shed door! Children can also manually spin the left and right doors to reveal different characters. Plus, when the circle is placed in the side shed, Sir Topham Hatt pops out! Featuring a convenient recessed back area for easy carrying, and a roof that flips open to remove or store the play pieces, the Tidmouth Shape Sorter delivers a valuable, interactive playtime experience for your child! Toddlers ages 12M+.

column6: Thomas & Friends™ Collectible Railway Thomas’ Great Dino Delivery
Thomas & Friends™ Motorized Railway Diesel’s Lift & Shift Set
column7: Thomas & Friends™ Toy Train  Set with Motorized Toy Train
column8:
Get ready for a fun-filled Thomas & Friends™ delivery adventure at the Dieselworks with Diesel’s Lift & Shift Set from Fisher-Price! Start by picking up the oil drum from the barrel loader. You can use the stop-track to stop Diesel in front, then tip the loader so the barrel rolls into his cargo car. With his cargo in tow, Diesel speeds ahead to the fueling station, where you can push the fuel nozzle down to stop him, and move the nozzle up to send him on his way. Next, when he races into the Dieselworks, the engine hoist lifts him and his cargo car, then amazingly transfers them to the other track! With a full track layout, two stop-tracks, and cool engine-lifting action, Diesel’s Lift & Shift Set helps you create a world of imaginative play while expanding your Thomas & Friends™ Motorized Railway! Children ages 3Y+.

Features
• Includes full track layout with multiple features and Diesel motorized toy train with cargo car and cargo
• Stop Diesel in front of barrel loader and tip the loader to roll barrel into his cargo car • Use fuel nozzle at fueling station to start and stop Diesel
• Cool engine hoist lifts Diesel and his cargo car, then transfers them to the other track
• Compatible with most Thomas & Friends™ Motorized Railway toy trains (additional trains sold separately)
• Requires 1 AAA battery
• Perfect addition to the your expandable Motorized Railway

column6: Thomas & Friends™ Motorized Railway Thomas’ Shipwreck Adventure
column7: Thomas & Friends™ Toy Train  Set with Motorized Toy Train
column8:
Inspired by the Thomas & Friends™ DVD movie, Sodor’s Legend of the Lost Treasure, Thomas is exploring an old shipwreck in this exciting Motorized Railway train set! Start Thomas near the yellow signal gantry and send him through the caution signs towards the shipwreck. As Thomas crosses the ship, the deck collapses and the big pirate flag pops up while a secret passage is revealed in the hull of the shipwreck! Below deck, Thomas pushes Skiff the rail-boat out from the bow towards Knapford Station. When Skiff enters the station, Sailor John pops out from behind the door and the treasure suddenly appears in Skiff’s stern! With the treasure, Thomas and Skiff race over the hill to the harbor, and as they crash into the water, the waves splash up around them! Use the directional switch to send them through the hull of the ship, or back up over the deck! Full of fun characters and thrilling action, Thomas’ Shipwreck Adventure brings the world of Thomas & Friends™ to life! Children ages 3Y+.

Features
• Inspired by the Thomas & Friends™ DVD movie, Sodor’s Legend of the Lost Treasure
• Includes full track layout with Thomas motorized toy train and rolling Skiff
• Features shipwreck with collapsing deck and pop-up pirate flag
• When Thomas reaches the harbor, the water splashes up around him
• Also includes signs, signal gantry, and station with Sailor John label art
• Compatible with most Thomas & Friends™ Motorized Railway toy trains (additional engines sold separately)
• Perfect addition to the your expandable Motorized Railway
• Requires 1 AAA battery

column7: Three levels of play with songs, phrases & sounds for your child’s age & stage!
column8:
It’s baby’s very own place to sit and discover new things—including ABCs, 1-2-3s, colors, shapes, and more! The “magic” seat knows whenever baby sits down or stands up, and it rewards baby with songs and phrases every time. Baby can also press the light-up remote or flip the book pages to hear over 50 sing-along songs, tunes and phrases…and lift seat “cushion” to find even more fun surprises underneath!

Smart Stages™ Chair includes Smart Stages™ technology, an exciting new way to change learning content as baby grows. Every baby develops at their own pace, and Smart Stages™ technology gives you the ability to select the stage that’s best for your child! There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play—just slide the switch, or enter baby’s age for automatic level changes.

Smart Stages™ Technology
Level 1 – Explore – 12M+
First words and sounds spark baby’s curiosity
Level 2 – Encourage – 18M+
Prompt baby though questions and simple directions
Level 3 – Pretend – 24M+
Imaginative fun and early role play

Features
• 50+ sing-along songs, tunes & phrases
• Includes Smart Stages™ technology – learning content changes as baby grows
• Three levels of play offer fresh songs, phrases & sounds for your little one’s age & stage
• Enter baby’s age for automatic Smart Stages™ level changes or manually change levels with the switch
• Seat activates songs & phrases when baby sits & stands
• Busy activities include an illustrated flip-book & light-up remote control with buttons to press
• Lift the seat for fun surprises
• Teaches first words, numbers, shapes, colors and more
• Requires 3 AA batteries

column8:
Thomas & Friends™ Collectible Mini Toy Train in Single Blind Pack

Thomas & Friends™ engines just got a mini makeover! With over 70 mini engines to collect, Thomas & Friends™ Minis from Fisher-Price completely reimagine the Island of Sodor with never-before-seen themes! From “Spooky” monsters and speedy “Racers”, to super-themed “Heroes” and prehistoric “Dino” engines, this collection of pintsized engines showcases Thomas & Friends™ in a whole new way! Of course, no collection is complete without your favorite characters in their classic styles, which is why Thomas & Friends™ Minis also include 30 classic engines in addition to over 40 themed engines.

This single blind pack contains one mystery character! After all, with a variety of unique engines to collect – some rarer than others – half the fun is guessing who’s hiding inside! Collect ’em, race ’em, trade ’em, and use your imagination to create really unique adventures for these Really Useful engines!

Features
• Single blind pack contains one mystery Thomas & Friends™ character
• Over 70 Thomas & Friends™ Minis to collect
• Never-before-seen themes and styles
• Look for more characters and themes as they’re introduced

Of course, no collection is complete without your child's favorite characters in their classic styles, which is why Thomas & Friends™ MINIS also include 30 classic engines in addition to over 40 themed engines. This single blind pack contains one mystery character. After all, with a variety of unique engines to collect – some rarer than others – half the fun is guessing who’s hiding inside! Collect ’em, race ’em, trade ’em, and let your child use their imagination to create really unique adventures for these Really Useful engines!

• Single blind pack contains one mystery Thomas & Friends™ character

• Never-before-seen themes and styles

Features
• Four brightly colored arches for stack-and-nest play
• Bat at the croc for fun rocking action!
• Figuring out how to stack arches from biggest to smallest, or nest them the opposite way, helps baby develop thinking and problem solving skills
• Stacking and nesting also help sharpen baby’s fine motor skills
• Introduces baby to colors, too

The wide, stable base and easy-grasp handle help steady first steps, and sweet music & lights accompany her as she strolls along. It’s an adorable way to encourage gross motor development and early role play – with lots of fun, hands-on activities, too.

A press of the “magic” wand button rewards baby with fun sounds. The clacker beads and butterfly flip book help foster fine motor skills, too. There’s even room for a Princess Chime doll or other favorite friend to push! (Doll sold separately and subject to availability.)

• Music and lights activate as baby walks
• Baby’s rewarded with fun songs & sounds when she presses the “magic” wand – a great first introduction to cause & effect!

column6: Laugh & Learn® Smart Stages™ Tablet - Gold
column7: Baby’s first tablet introduces letters, first words, animals and more!
column8:
Introducing Baby’s very own tablet—the Fisher-Price® Laugh & Learn® Smart Stages™ Tablet! This tablet includes Smart Stages™ technology, an exciting new way to change the learning content as baby grows! Because every baby develops at their own pace, Smart Stages™ technology gives you the ability to select the stage that’s best for your child! There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play. Baby can press one of 28 “app” buttons to activate sounds and music – and unlock learning about letters, first words, animals and more. To add even more fun, the tablet screen will light up and twinkle along to the songs and phrases.

Features
• Introduces Baby to letters, first words, animals and more!
• Lots of music, phrases and fun sounds!
• Includes Smart Stages™ technology—learning changes as baby grows!
• Three levels of play offer fresh songs, phrases and sounds for your little one
• Requires 3 AA batteries
• Available in 4 different colors!

Level 1 – Explore – 12M+
Hands-on exploration rewards baby with fun sounds, phrases and sing-along songs. Baby can press any of the ABC buttons to hear first words like, “cookie.”

Level 2 – Encourage – 18M+
This level encourages baby to find letters and objects! Music, sounds and voice phrases reward baby for playing. Press buttons to hear prompts like, “Find monkey.”

Level 3 – Pretend – 24M+
Just like a real tablet—but even more fun! Realistic flat-screen tablet encourages imitation and imagination through early role play. “Neighhhh! Can you neigh like a horse?”

column7: Kids get the fun rollin’ at the Little People® Rollin’ Ramps Garage!
column8:
Need a tune-up? A fuel-up? A ramp to ZOOM down? Then head on over to the Little People® Rollin’ Ramps Garage! Place Koby and his car on the elevator and take it to the top to park. Or, flip the gate and ZOOM down the ramps! You’re back on the first floor, so drive over to the gas pump to fuel up.

Press the button for fun garage sounds, like “glug-glug” as you fill your tank. And when it’s time for a tune-up, stop at the service station on the second floor and put the car on the mechanic’s lift to check it out!

• Flip up the gate and zoom down the ramp!
• Working elevator-- for car and driver!
• Press buttons at gas pump for fun sounds!
• Plenty of room to park at the top
• Includes Koby and his car

Easy-access control panel faces out, framed by neutral home decor fabric to subtly complement baby’s nursery.

- Twinkling light show
- Tracking light show
- Lights out
• Plays up to 30 minutes of soothing music, white noise & nature sounds
• Lights, sounds & music help soothe & comfort baby in the crib
• After 5 minutes the light show slows down to reduce stimulation and lull baby to sleep
• Animal friends help comfort & entertain

column7: Has BATMAN™ met his match with MAN-BAT?

Man-Bat’s wing span is HUGE, with shoulder, forearm, neck and leg joints that move so he can “fly”! BATMAN, ROBIN and other GOTHAM CITY Super Heroes better watch out! He can hold a figure in each hand. (Figures sold separately and subject to availability.) And when kids push the button on his back, he’ll shake his wings and make a fast getaway! But is he in for a big comedown? That’s up to little crime-fighters to decide!

• Man-Bat’s ready for action, with moveable shoulder, forearm, neck and leg joints

There’s even a projectile launcher and 2 “water” projectiles to battle even the toughest pretend blaze!

What a great way to spark kids’ imaginations, especially if they have a firefighter in the family!

With a canopy that opens and closes to fit all standard Imaginext® DC Super Friends™ figures (sold separately), kids will be launching new adventures every day!

And when things really heat up, he can launch “water” disks from the belly of the Mech suit!

With 4 poseable legs, 2 poseable arms, and a waist that twists left or right, the Fire Mech Suit is ready to move on any futuristic rescue adventure your little firefighter can think up!

• Open and close canopy on the suit to place firefighter figure inside

• Snap the saw accessory onto the back of the Mech Suit or on the suit’s forearm
• Includes the Imaginext® Fire Mech Suit, firefighter figure with removable armor, 3 “water” disks and saw

Thomas & Friends™ Collectible Mini Toy Train in Single Blind Pack

Thomas & Friends™ engines just got a mini makeover! With over 70 mini engines to collect, Thomas & Friends™ Minis from Fisher-Price completely reimagine the Island of Sodor with never-before-seen themes! From “Spooky” monsters and speedy “Racers”, to super-themed “Heroes” and prehistoric “Dino” engines, this collection of pintsized engines showcases Thomas & Friends™ in a whole new way! Of course, no collection is complete without your favorite characters in their classic styles, which is why Thomas & Friends™ Minis also include 30 classic engines in addition to over 40 themed engines.

This single blind pack contains one mystery character! After all, with a variety of unique engines to collect – some rarer than others – half the fun is guessing who’s hiding inside! Collect ’em, race ’em, trade ’em, and use your imagination to create really unique adventures for these Really Useful engines!

Features
• Single blind pack contains one mystery Thomas & Friends™ character
• Over 70 Thomas & Friends™ Minis to collect
• Never-before-seen themes and styles
• Look for more characters and themes as they’re introduced

Age Grade - 3Y+

column6: My Little Snugabear Ballerina Cradle ’n Swing
column7: Soothing baby swing swings 2 ways: rocks side-to-side like a cradle & swings head-to-toe!
column8:
Deluxe baby swing features and pink/grey fabrics make Fisher-Price® My Little Snugabear Ballerina Cradle ’n Swing soft and soothing—just like a little bear hug!—with two different swinging motions and a variety of other customizable features that let you choose and combine what baby likes best! SmartSwing Technology offers six different baby swing speeds from low to high—whether baby is rocking side-to-side, or swinging head-to-toe. It’s easy to switch from one swing motion to another; just push a button and turn the seat! My Little Snugabear cradle swing actually senses baby’s weight, so speeds won’t slow as baby grows, and it starts without a push. The motorized mobile helps soothe baby, too, with 16 songs, nature sounds and three adorable ballerina bear friends that “dance” overhead to encourage eye-tracking and keep baby entertained. And the mirrored globe in the center of the mobile lets baby see all around the room! The deep, cozy seat with machine-washable padded seat cover has a linkable rattle toy, and a machine-washable body insert and head support for newborns, infants and smaller babies. My Little Snugabear Cradle ’n Swing is easy to assemble, with legs that fold for storage or portable room-to-room use. Two convenient power options make My Little Snugabear Cradle ’n Swing easy to use anywhere around the house. Plug it in for battery-free baby swing operation when you’re near an outlet, or switch to battery power swinging when you’re not!

Features
• Two swing motions to help soothe baby: rock baby side-to-side like a cradle or swing head-to-toe
• Fisher-Price® SmartSwing Technology
• Six swing speeds, 16 songs, soothing nature sounds
• Motorized mobile with mirrored globe and three ballerina bear mobile toys
• Two-position recline with 3 adjustable seat positions: right-facing, center, left-facing
• Easy to convert to different positions—just press button and turn
• Deep & cozy Papasan-style seat
• Machine-washable seat cover with deluxe My Little Snugabear body insert and head support
• Plush, snuggly fabrics with airy canopy
• Linkable rattle toy detaches for take along
• Easy to assemble
• Legs fold for storage and portable room-to-room use
• Two power options: plug in or battery-powered
• Includes AC adapter or requires 4 D alkaline batteries

Maximum Weightt: 25 lbs. (11,3 kg)

There’s a colorful, light-up rainbow-key piano to play, a bobble frog teether to chew on, a clacker ring bar to slide 3 colorful rings back and forth, and a turtle to click-click-click! And that’s not all! Baby’s natural jumping and kicking actions send the seat bouncing up and down for a really fun and exciting ride – and baby’s jumping is rewarded with lights, sounds and music! The sturdy Jumperoo® frame is free-standing for convenience (it won’t block a doorway!), height-adjustable (so it “grows” with baby!), and it’s easy to fold flat for portability and space saving storage (with the removable toy bar stored flat, too!). column7: Help soothe baby with a gentle rock or glide, head-to-toe or side-to-side!
column8:
Most babies love the soothing comfort and motion of being rocked and cradled in mom’s arms. That’s why, with 4 soothing rock and glide motions, calming vibrations, and a soft, padded seat, Fisher-Price® 4-in-1 Rock ’n Glide Soother was designed to mimic the soothing motion and comfort of baby being cradled, rocked, and soothed. It’s actually two babygear must-haves in one—with four different ways to move (and help soothe) baby! Baby can rock or glide head-to-toe or side-to-side, with optional, battery-powered calming vibrations. Just choose rock or glide mode, then turn the rock & glide seat to select head-to-toe or side-to-side motion. (The seat rotates 360° degrees, so it’s easy to keep baby in sight!) Convenient foot pedal operation lets you quickly turn AC-powered gliding motion on or off; music and nature sounds help soothe and comfort baby, too! It’s quick and easy to convert 4-in-1 Rock ’n Glide Soother from a powered glider to a cozy cradle rocker—just lift the calming vibrations rocker seat from the glider base. The portable seat with removable newborn head and body support insert adjusts to 2 different rock ’n glide positions, so it grows with baby from newborn, to infant, to older baby. Choose reclined for newborns, infants, and soothing or napping; or inclined for older babies and play time! The removable toy bar keeps baby entertained with two soft toys overhead, with a linkable fox blankie with satin-tipped tail for hands-on fun, too!

Features
• Four different rock ’n glide motions help soothe baby
• Rocks or glides head-to-toe or side-to-side
• Three gliding speeds and two reclining positions
• Calming vibrations
• 12 songs & 3 soothing nature sound effects
• Seat easily removes to go from glider to rocker
• Removable toy bar with soft fox toys keeps baby entertained
• Linkable fox blankie with satin-tipped tail
• Machine-washable soft-fabric seat pad and infant body & head support
• Seat handles for easy room-to-room portability
• Easy to assemble
• Includes AC adapter for glider
• Requires 1 D battery for calming vibrations

Age Grade Maximum weight: 25 lbs (11,3 kg)

Developmental Statement Use from birth until child is able to sit up unassisted.

column7: All abooooard for fun with this motorized train set featuring a mountain with boulder drop, bridge, loading depot, working crane & lots of track.
column8:
This motorized train set is engineered for little ones to set up and play all by themselves. The EZ Snap Track is a “snap” to put together – and there’s lots of it (over 18 feet, in fact) so young conductors can build it their way. Now get ready to roll! First stop is the EZ Load Station that makes getting cars on the track easy for little hands. Chugga! Chugga! The train’s on its way…with realistic engine sounds and working lights! Kids will love watching the motorized Santa Fe train travel over the bridge, around the curves and through the mountain tunnel. Watch out below! Kids can send a boulder dropping from the top of the mountain. And they can head to the depot to load and unload cargo with the working crane. With so much to keep young hands & minds busy all the livelong day, this EZ Play Railway train set is a great way to rev up fine motor skills and young imaginations.

• Motorized train set is EZ to build, load & use – everything kids need to play right away
• EZ Load Station makes putting cars on the tracks easy-peasy for little ones
• Motorized train with working lights, fun engine sounds & EZ start/stop
• Mountain with fun boulder drop
• Loading depot with working crane to load & unload cargo
• Bridge takes the fun to a whole new level
• Track switchers let kids go a different way each time they play!
• Includes 52 pieces: motorized Santa Fe train with 2 cars, over 18 feet of track, mountain, bridge & loading depot, track accessories and 4 bridge trestles

This product is sold exclusively at Toys R Us and FAO Schwarz

• Buddy Pack includes 4 characters from Disney’s Aladdin: Jasmine, Aladdin, Genie & Rajah
• Little People® figures are kid-sized for small hands
• Bring Jasmine to the Disney Princess Songs Palace by Little People® to hear her sing and talk (Palace sold separately and subject to availability.)

©Disney Visit www.disney.com

column7: This baby gym, with music & lights, extra-large mat, premium fabrics, tummy wedge & calming vibrations, helps exercise developmental skills!
column8:
Your little wiggle worm has lots of room to explore on this stylish gym, designed in partnership with Jonathan Adler. The extra-large mat is full of big fun, with 9 linkable toys and a variety of textures and sounds to discover. Newborns can lay & play, watching the "dancing" colored lights & mobile overhead and batting at the colorful toys.

As baby grows, encourage tummy time play by moving the toys to the mat and making your little one comfy with the tummy wedge that provides 10 minutes of calming vibrations. And don't leave all the fun behind - remove the soft mobile and attach it to baby's stroller for on-the-go play! With so much to see, hear and do, including short play and long play music (up to 20 minutes), this will be baby's new favorite place to play!

Where development comes into play™
Fine Motor: Grasping rattles and clackers fosters fine motor skills & eye-hand coordination.

Gross Motor: Fosters gross motor skills when baby kicks-at, bats-at, shakes, and reaches for the toys & activities.

• 9 linkable activity toys, including a mirror for self-discovery
• Tummy wedge with 10 minutes of calming vibrations
• Soft overhead mobile removes for stroller play when you're on the go-go-go!
• Overhead mobile and 4 colored lights that "dance" to the beat encourage eye tracking
• Short play & long play music - up to 20 minutes
• Extra-large mat is extra-comfy, with premium plush fabrics

column6: Moonlight Meadow Smart Connect™ 2-in-1 Projection Mobile
column7: Control mobile action, calming music and soothing lights from your smart device!
Link up with these fun pals that have silly sounds & busy activities – and go everywhere you and baby go!
column8:
These adorable activity toys are ready to hang with baby and keep your little cuddle bug entertained when you’re on the go-go-go! (And when aren’t you?) Just use the links to easily clip the 3 animal characters to a stroller or diaper bag – and let them do their thing!

The cute lion friend makes fun jingle sounds and his soft legs are loops to hang other toys on. The caterpillar has 3 clackers for baby to spin. And the ladybug mirror invites self-discovery.

• 3 fun animal characters to link up & go: jingle lion, ladybug mirror & clacker caterpillar
• Busy, busy! Activity toys offer lots of hands-on play for baby
• 3 removable activity links – great for on-the-go!
• Helps exercise baby’s fine motor skills
• Bright colors & fun sounds help to strengthen important senses like sight & hearing

column6: Magic of Disney Minnie & Daisy Buddy Pack by Little People®
column7: Experience the magic of Minnie Mouse & Daisy Duck Disney figures.
column8:
You can rest easy that two of Disney’s best-loved characters are in good hands. (That’s because they’re sized just right to fit in your toddler’s hands!) In this Disney classic figure 2-pack, Minnie with her camera and Daisy with her ice cream cone are ready for a day of magical fun and adventure wherever your little one decides to take them.

• When these two get together, it’s Disney magic
• Double the fun! 2-pack includes Minnie figure with a camera and Daisy figure with ice cream cone
• Bring them to the Magic of Disney Day at Disney by Little People® play set(Play set sold separately and subject to availability.)

column7: Rattle! Jingle! Clack! This linkable 5-toy activity set has everything baby needs for hands-on, sensory, skill-building play.
column8:
Entertain busy little babies with this linkable, 5-toy activity set. Hands-on activities include a soft jingle hedgehog, a self-discovery mirror with satiny back (so smooth!), turtle and mushroom rattles and lizard clackers. Bring your own toys to the playtime party – there are extra loops on the hedgehog’s legs for linking and take-along.

• Soft, tactile hedgehog – shake for jingle sounds!
• Self-discovery mirror with satiny back
• Turtle rattle
• Mushroom rattle
• Lizard clackers
• Hedgehog legs are loops for linking toys
• Great for playtime at home or entertaining baby on the go

column7: Look familiar? It’s a Fisher-Price® fave – the classic Rock-A-Stack® - redesigned as a newborn-sized rattle.
column8:
So much classic fun for your little one! Sized just-right for baby’s hands, this Rock-A-Stack® clacker rattle features brightly colored rings, fun clacking and rattle sounds. Great for giving your child’s senses a boost.

• Baby-appropriate clacker inspired by the classic Rock-a-Stack®
• Clacker and rattle sounds
• Colorful rings
• Sized for baby’s hands to shake and hold
• Great for stimulating baby’s senses
• Entertain newborns at home or on the go

column6: Baby's First Car Grow with Me Gym

column7: Look familiar? It’s a Fisher-Price® fave – the classic camera – with soft crinkle textures, perfect for newborn babies.
column8:
So much classic fun for your little one! Sized just-right for baby’s hands, this soft camera features a self-discovery mirror and crinkle textures for sensory stimulation. The chewy flash cube is designed for teething. Say cheese, and take it on the go!

• Newborn appropriate camera toy inspired by the classic Fisher-Price® Camera
• Fun crinkle sounds
• Mirror for self-discovery
• Chewy flash cube
• Loop for playtime on the go
• Entertain newborns at home or on the go
• Encourages developing senses

column7: This toy lion provides BIG animal fun, with fun sounds & realistic movements to make kids’ imaginations go wild!
column8:
Pretend play comes roaring to life with the Little People® Lion. He’s “life-sized” (compared to other Little People® figures, that is) with fun sounds and movements that make the play more real. Open his mouth to hear him roar. Close his mouth and hear him “slurp, slurp” as he takes a drink at the water trough. Lay him on his side and he’ll start snoring! And when kids stand him up again after his “cat” nap, he makes grumbling sounds. What a great way to introduce little ones to the wonders of the animal kingdom!

• “Roar!” “Slurp!” “Zzzz!” Open & close the lion’s mouth or lay him on his side to activate fun sounds!
• Movable head and legs make the play more real – and more fun, too!
• Includes Little People® Lion, trainer figure and water trough.

column7: Little People® figures put a whole community of friends & neighbors right at your toddler’s fingertips!
column8:
The Little People® Artist figure has paint palette and brush in hand to create her next masterpiece. And she’s not too big, not too small, but ahhh…just the right size to fit in toddlers’ hands for easy grasping and handling. You can use Little People® toys like the Artist to help kids discover and explore the big world around them.

• Expand your toddler’s world with the Little People® Artist figure
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!
• Bring her to any Little People® playset to add to the fun – and be sure to bring other Little People® friends along, too! (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)

column7: Little People® figures put a whole community of friends, neighbors & relatives right at your toddler’s fingertips!
column8:
Great Grandma has just baked a pie while Great Grandpa and puppy wait patiently to get a slice. These sweet Little People® figures are not too big, not too small, but ahhh…just the right size to fit in toddlers’ hands for easy grasping and handling. You can use Little People® toys like these to help kids discover and explore the big world around them.

• Expand your toddler’s world with the Little People® Great Grandma & Grandpa figures
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!
• Bring them to any Little People® playset to add to the fun – and be sure to bring other Little People® friends along, too! (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)

column6: Disney Princess Rapunzel & Friends by Little People®
column7: Recreate Rapunzel’s magical story with these 4 Little People® figures!
column8:
The tale of Disney Princess Rapunzel wouldn’t be complete without Rapunzel (holding a paint palette), Flynn Rider, her horse Maximus (which the figures can ride), and Pascal the chameleon. Little ones can use these Little People® figures to retell the beloved story of Rapunzel – or create new adventures of their own!

• 4-pack includes Disney Princess Rapunzel, Flynn Rider, Maximus and Pascal figures by Little People®
• Rapunzel and Flynn figures fit on Maximus the horse
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!

©Disney

column6: DOLL SCRAPBOOK: STYLE A CREATIVE KEEPSAKE FOR YOUR SPECIAL FRIEND
Magic of Disney Swirlin Umbrella Minnie by Little People®
column8:
Little ones will love rolling Minnie’s red car along and watching her umbrella twirl as she goes. Flip up the heart-shaped trunk to see what Minnie is bringing with her – looks like she brought an extra pair of shoes, sunglasses and jewelry along for the ride! So where’s she headed? Mickey Mouse’s house? Running errands? Or just out for a fun day on the town? That’s up to young imaginations to decide as they steer one magical adventure after another!

• Give it a whirl! Roll Minnie’s car along to see the umbrella spin
• Flip up heart-shaped trunk to see what’s inside
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!
• Includes car and Disney Minnie figure by Little People®

©Disney Visit www.disney.com

column6: Magic of Disney Magical Day at Disney by Little People®
column8:
Kids will love discovering the magic of Disney at the Magical Day at Disney playset by Little People®! Start the day by putting Mickey Mouse or Minnie Mouse on the train and rolling it down the ramp. When it bursts through the door at the bottom, hear fun sounds & phrases from Mickey. Now they're off to the spinning Dumbo ride or the food court to grab a quick snack.

The hands-on fun is everywhere! Spin Tinker Bell to make her "fly" overhead – or press the button on the ice cream cart to see Donald pop up. There's so much to see and do as little ones create their own Disney adventures with Mickey & Minnie over and over (and over) again!

• Get the fun rolling! Roll the train down the ramp
• Watch out below! Burst through the door at the bottom to hear fun sounds & phrases from Mickey
• Spin Tinker Bell to watch her “fly” overhead
• Take a spin on the Dumbo ride
• Peek-a-boo! Push button on cart to make Donald pop up
• Includes Disney Minnie & Mickey figures by Little People®, 2 chairs, a table and train
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!

©Disney

column7: These Little People® figures put all kinds of fun camping adventures in kids’ hands!
column8:
Koby’s got his binoculars on and he’s looking for adventure. What does he spy with his little eye? It’s an adorable baby bear who’s ready to romp and play in the woods all day! They’re a wildly wonderful addition to the Little People® Songs & Sounds Camper or Going Camping set.

• Includes Little People® Koby and bear figures
• Little People® figures are kid-sized – perfect for kid-sized hands!

column6: Barbie® Nikki™ Doll and Daybed Set
Thomas & Friends™ Wooden Railway Seaside Sidney
column8:
A Wooden Railway engine of Sidney with a seaside design.

Thomas & Friends™ Wooden Railway Seaside Sidney is busy working near the docks and helping to keep things running at the Sodor Aquarium! Play out fun storylines of Sidney making special feed deliveries to the Sodor Shark Exhibit or the Leap & Splash Dolphin Rescue sets (sold separately and subject to availability). Seaside Sidney can connect to other Wooden Railway trains with magnet connectors. Perfect for Thomas & Friends™ Wooden Railway train sets (sold separately and subject to availability)!

Features

• Magnets let you attach other Wooden Railway train engines or tenders (sold separately and subject to availability)

column6: Imaginext® SPONGEBOB™ Bikini Bottom Police Station and Jail
column7: Kids can keep order afloat in Bikini Bottom with this fun play set!
column8:
Unlock kids’ imagination and all kinds of wacky Bikini Bottom adventures with this Police Station & Jail play set that’s supervised by police captain SpongeBob SquarePants! To lock up criminals, sail them to jail by boat! Simply turn SpongeBob on the Power Pad to send the boat sailing to the jail cell to drop off the prisoner! Then turn SpongeBob back on the Power Pad to pull the boat back and slam the jail door shut!

And because it is Bikini Bottom, this jail is equipped with a spatula launcher to release prisoners from custody. (Just turn the 2nd Power Pad to activate the launcher.) And what if a prisoner escapes? Just push a button to launch the tethered projectile at him and reel him in! There’s also a jail cell ball that opens & closes and 2 ladders on back to help kids create a tidal wave of Bikini Bottom adventures! Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Turn 1st Power Pad to sail boat to jail & dump off prisoner; turn it again to pull boat back & close jail door
• Turn 2nd Power Pad to activate spatula launcher – door below will open & “kick” prisoner out!
• Push button to fire tethered projectile launcher at escaping prisoners!
• Jail cell ball opens & closes to hold figures
• Also features 2 ladders on back so figures can access all play set levels
• Includes Police Station & Jail play set, SpongeBob™ police figure, fish prisoner figure & 1 projectile

This product is sold exclusively at Toys R Us.

column6: Imaginext® SPONGEBOB™ Man Ray and Hot Rod
column7: Man Ray is steering some E.V.I.L. plots against SpongeBob and friends!
column8:
Man Ray and Dirty Bubble, arch enemies of Mermaid Man & Barnacle Boy and creators of E.V.I.L. (Every Villain is Lemons), are stirring up trouble with this projectile-launching Hot Rod! Kids can open the canopy of the Hot Rod and put Man Ray in the driver’s seat. A turn of the Power Pad sets off the car horn and launches projectiles from the front of the Hot Rod! And it really rolls, too! SpongeBob and his friends better watch out! It’s the perfect toy vehicle for creating wild Bikini Bottom adventures – and revving up kids’ imaginations!

• Turn Power Pad in driver’s seat to honk horn and fire projectiles!
• Roll the Hot Rod from one Bikini Bottom adventure to the next!
• Includes Hot Rod, Man Ray and Dirty Bubble figures, and 2 projectiles

column6: Imaginext® SPONGEBOB™ Super Hero SpongeBob and Patrick
column8:
SpongeBob & Patrick are superheroes, ready to save the day – and the Krabby Patty recipe!

These SpongeBob & Patrick figures are dressed as superheroes – SpongeBob in a blue cape and Patrick in a green cape, armed with a spatula! They’re all geared up to do battle with E.V.I.L. forces like Man Ray and Dirty Bubble and protect the Krabby Patty recipe, too! (It’s all in a day’s work for superheroes, after all!) Kids get to use their greatest super power – imagination – to create wild & wacky Bikini Bottom adventures for these action figures!

• Includes Superhero SpongeBob in blue cape and Superhero Patrick figure in green cape with spatula
• Use these figures with other Imaginext® SpongeBob SquarePants figures, vehicles & playsets to create exciting Bikini Bottom adventures! (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)

column6: Imaginext® SPONGEBOB™ Caveman SpongeBob and Patrick
column8:
SpongeBob & Patrick are cavemen in prehistoric Bikini Bottom!

In an epic SpongeBob SquarePants episode, SpongeBob and Patrick are Neanderthal friends in prehistoric Bikini Bottom who discover fire after an underwater thunderstorm – and battle over who should control it! Kids will love using these figures to recreate favorite SpongeBob SquarePants show scenes – or creating new prehistoric hysterics of their own!

• Includes Caveman SpongeBob figure with club and Caveman Patrick figure with fire piece
• Use these figures with other Imaginext® SpongeBob SquarePants figures, vehicles and play sets to create exciting Bikini Bottom adventures! (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)

column6: Imaginext® Deep Sea Mission Command Boat
column7: Your mission (if you decide to accept it)…defend this awesome toy boat and defeat the giant squid! Aye, aye captain!
column8:
This toy ship is loaded with everything kids need to get their imaginations moving full speed ahead into exciting deep-sea rescue adventures! It features 3 Power Pads to bring the action to life. Turn the 1st Power Pad to the right to open the hull and reveal the ocean rescue lab – or turn it to the left to drop barrels onto menacing sea creatures! Turn the 2nd Power Pad to rotate the boat’s crane – and use the lever to load or unload cargo. Look out…a giant squid is about to attack! Turn the 3rd Power Pad to aim the projectile launcher – and pull back the lever to fire!

Need more help? Send the mini-sub with projectile launchers to capture the squid and bring it on deck for observation! And when the mission’s complete, everything stores on board until the next attack by a giant squid – or other scary creature like big brother!

• Turn 1st Power Pad to right for an awesome transformation – hull opens and a whole ocean rescue lab is revealed!
• Turn 1st Power to left to drop barrels from back
• Turn 2nd Power Pad to rotate crane – and press lever to load cargo with crane’s hook
• Turn 3rd Power Pad to aim projectile launcher – and pull back on lever to fire!
• Remove mini-sub from hull for deep-sea rescues and added fire power
• Includes Deep Sea Mission Command Boat, 2 figures with dive armor, mini-sub, 4 projectiles, 3 barrels & giant squid with mouth that opens & closes
• Easy clean-up - everything stores on boat to make captain mom & dad happy!

column7: Kids can go “crabbing” on the beach with this 6-Wheeler! Crabs included!
column8:
How many ways are there to catch a crab? Two…if you have this awesome 6-Wheeler to help you! Turn the Power Pad to activate the crab rake and lower the ramp on back. Return the Power Pad to its original position and you can scoop up a crab! Look…there’s another crab! Pull out the hook from the front bumper, which splits open to look like two crab claws. Just hook a crab on the line and roll the 6-Wheeler backward to rewind the hook and close the claws. Just add sand, dirt and a little imagination – and kids will love digging up lots of new adventures catching crabs and who knows what else! Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Turn Power Pad in 6-Wheeler to deploy crab rake and drop the ramp!
• Return Power Pad to its original position to scoop crab into back!
• To catch another crab, pull out hook from front bumper, hook crab on line and back up ATV to rewind hook and close claws
• Figure fits in driver’s seat
• Includes 6-Wheeler, 1 figure and 2 crabs

column7: Shark attack! With pop-out claw and projectile launchers, this toy sub can handle any deep-sea danger (or sibling threat) kids can imagine!
column8:
Kids can dive deep…deep…deep into their imaginations to create awesome adventures for this toy submarine! Turn the Power Pad to the right to make a claw pop out from the back. Or turn it to the left to open the canopy and place the deep-sea diver figure in the cockpit. Look out…there’s a shark circling! Push button to fire projectiles from the removable fins below the toy sub. Whew, that was close! Will that wily shark get you next time? Only little captains know for sure! Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Turn Power Pad to right to pop out back claw
• Turn Power Pad to left to open canopy and put figure in cockpit
• Push button to fire projectiles from removable fins
• Includes Deep Sea Sub, shark, diver figure with scuba armor and 4 projectiles

column7: The Imaginext® Wind Jammer comes to the rescue after a manta ray attack!
column8:
Help! A manta ray has attacked a swimmer in the ocean! Send this Imaginext® windsurfer figure on his rolling Wind Jammer board to save the day! Just push a button on the back of the Wind Jammer to launch a life canister to the victim, while the windsurfer tries to free him from the manta ray. Both the manta ray and life canister fit on any Imaginext® figure. (Windsurfer figure included; additional figures sold separately.) Kids will create rescue adventures for this figure pack that are as limitless as the ocean – and their own imaginations! Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Push button on back of Wind Jammer to launch life canister
• Includes rolling Wind Jammer, windsurfer figure, and life jacket, life canister and manta ray that fit on any Imaginext® figure! (Additional figures sold separately and subject to availability.)

column7: Make ocean adventures more “electrifying” with this Mini Sub and glow-in-the-dark eel!
column8:
An “electric” eel is about to attack the Imaginext® Mini Sub and its captain! No worries…press a button to spin the Mini Sub’s propeller for a fast getaway. And if the eel chases after, fire a projectile to stop it! Whew…that was close! But don’t relax yet. The glow-in-the-dark eel can latch onto the captain’s arm & leg when he’s not looking! Kids will use this figure pack – and their imaginations – to dive into all kinds of exciting ocean adventures! Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Press button on side of the Mini Sub to spin the propeller and fire projectile
• Eel glows in the dark and fits on figure’s arm & leg
• Includes Mini Sub, captain figure, life jacket accessory, eel and 1 projectile

Help Inkling rescue the mimic octopus!

When a mimic octopus loses his way, it’s up to Inkling to save the day! Kids can pretend Inkling can use his special Octo-Suit to control the Octopod remotely and alert the crew to the new rescue! Includes an Inkling figure and a mimic octopus to rescue!

Features
• Features Inkling in his Octo-suit! On the show Inkling uses this special suit to control the Octopod remotely!
• Includes a mimic octopus to rescue!

Help Kwazii recover his spyglass from the slime eel!

It’s slime time! Kwazii is searching a shipwreck for his grandfather’s long-lost spyglass but he must be very careful—the golden spyglass is guarded by a sentinel slime eel! Includes Kwazii, his spyglass and a slime eel!


• Uh-oh! This rescue could get super slimy! Kwazii must rescue his grandfather’s spyglass which is guarded by a slime eel!
• Includes Kwazii, spyglass and slime eel.

Join Tweak on a super-slimy swamp adventure!

It’s slime time! Tweak is tracking a baby flamingo that has lost its way in the slimy swamp, so it’s a good thing she’s got all the right gear for her rescue! She can use her handy heli-pack to reach the creature quickly or use her swamp stilts to wade through the mucky marsh—a packet of ooey, gooey, sticky swamp slime is included! With her rescue gear, transport basket and interchangeable helmets, Tweak has everything she needs to rescue the flamingo faster than you can say, “Buncha munchy, crunchy carrots!” Includes Tweak, flamingo, three helmets, heli-pack, swamp stilts, basket and a container of sea slime.

Features
• Help Tweak rescue the baby flamingo lost in the swamp!
• Includes sticky swamp slime! Create a swampy slime environment with the included ooey, green goo!
• Swamp stilts are ideal for wading through the swamp slime!
• The heli-pack is just the thing to get a better view!
• Includes three interchangeable helmets suitable for any rescue mission!

Join Kwazii on a shark adventure!

When Kwazii discovers a lost dwarf lantern shark, he must help his new (and very hungry!) friend find food! Kwazii can safely send a snack to his famished friend with the fish biscuit launcher or if he’s feeling even more daring than usual, he can get a closer look with his Octo-goggles! Includes Kwazii, three diving helmets, fish biscuit launcher, three fish biscuits and a dwarf lantern shark to rescue.

Features
• Help Kwazii rescue the lost dwarf lantern shark!
• Feed the hungry shark a fish biscuit with the included launcher!
• Interchangeable diving helmets suitable for any rescue mission!

The Octonauts’ remote-controlled Gup-B!

Deploy the super-speedy Gup-B when your mission requires a vehicle capable of reaching creatures quickly! This remote-controlled Gup puts the action in your hands! Drive the Gup forward to race to the rescue or spin in reverse when you need to double-back to a location! The Gup-B fits most of the Fisher-Price® Octonauts™ figures (sold separately) so you can collect the whole crew and complete more exciting missions! Includes Gup-B and remote control. On the television show the Octonauts’ missions take place in the water, but this Gup-B toy needs to stay on land. It is not intended for water play.

Features
• Get ready for exciting new adventures with a remote-controlled Gup-B!
• Remote allows you to drive the Gup forward or spin in reverse!

The Octonauts’ remote-controlled Gup-A!

Suitable for all sorts of rescue missions, the Gup-A will always get you where you need to go! This remote-controlled Gup puts the action in your hands! Drive the Gup forward to race to the rescue or spin in reverse when you need to double-back to a location! The Gup-A fits most of the Fisher-Price® Octonauts™ figures (sold separately) so you can collect the whole crew and complete more exciting missions! Includes Gup-A and remote control. On the television show the Octonauts’ missions take place in the water, but this Gup-A toy needs to stay on land. It is not intended for water play.

Features
• Get ready for exciting new adventures with a remote-controlled Gup-A!
• Remote allows you to drive the Gup forward or spin in reverse!

column8:
Get ready for more Octonauts adventures with the Gup-I Transforming Polar Vehicle!

The Gup-I is inspired by the durability and adaptability of the water bear. Part polar exploration station and part rugged vehicle, this Gup-I is equipped with everything the Octonauts need for creature rescues despite the worst of weather conditions. This transforming Gup features 3 ways to play! In Water Bear Mode, the Gup-I is in a horizontal position, allowing the Octonauts to explore or race to the rescue! In Scout Mode, the Gup-I can stand upright, giving the team the perfect view to scan and spot creatures from afar. In Command Center Mode, the Gup-I opens to reveal everything the Octonauts need for their rescues! The Gup-I comes with Kwazii in his snowsuit, an Adelie penguin to rescue and a satellite dish play piece. Not intended for water play. 3+

Features
• The Gup-I transforms for 3 ways to play!
• In Water Bear Mode the Gup-I can race and roll to the rescue!
• In Scout Mode, the Gup-I stands upright, giving the crew a better view to scan and spot creatures in trouble!
• In Command Center Mode, the Gup-I opens to reveal everything the Octonauts need for their rescues!
• The Gup I comes with Kwazii in his snowsuit, an Adelie penguin to rescue and a satellite dish play piece.

column7: A die-cast engine of Racing Vinnie (from North America), inspired by the upcoming Thomas and Friends™ DVD, The Great Race.
column8:
Inspired by the character seen in the upcoming DVD, The Great Race, Thomas and Friends™ Take-n-Play™ Racing Vinnie is a North American engine with a tough demeanor and competitive drive that often get the better of him. While this makes it hard for the others to get along with him, they still lend him a hand in a time of need. He is a durable die-cast engine that features magnets which allow you to connect other Take-n-Play™ engines or tenders. Perfect for Take-n-Play™ Portable Fold-Out Playsets (sold separately and subject to availability)!

Features
• Durable die-cast Racing Vinnie engine
• Inspired by character from upcoming DVD, The Great Race
• Magnets let you attach to other engines, vehicles or tenders
• Works with Take-n-Play™ train sets (sold separately and subject to availability)
• May help develop gross motor skills, sensory skills and reasoning skills

column6: Thomas & Friends™ Take-n-Play™ Shooting Star Gordon
column8:
A streamlined, die-cast engine of Shooting Star Gordon, inspired by the upcoming Thomas and Friends™ DVD, The Great Race.

Inspired by the character featured in the upcoming DVD, The Great Race, Gordon is streamlined and ready for the race! His sleek shooting star design and determined face make him all the more dynamic. Shooting Star Gordon is a durable die-cast engine that features magnets which allow you to connect other Take-n-Play™ engines or tenders. Perfect for Take-n-Play™ Portable Fold-Out Playsets (sold separately and subject to availability)!

Features
• Durable and streamlined die-cast Gordon engine
• Includes tender
• Inspired by character from upcoming DVD, The Great Race
• Features a dynamic design
• Magnets let you attach to other engines, vehicles or tenders
• Works with Take-n-Play™ train sets (sold separately and subject to availability)

column6: Imaginext® DC Super Friends™ The Joker & Garbage Truck
column7: The Joker is up to some real “dirty” tricks, trashing Gotham City with his barrel-shooting Garbage Truck!
column8:
The Joker is creating merry mayhem in Gotham City again! He loads a barrel into his Garbage Truck and turns the dial to send it shooting out the back. (Just for laughs, of course!) Does The Joker have more “dirty” tricks planned as he cruises around Gotham City in his Garbage Truck? That’s up to kids’ imaginations to see who gets the last laugh!

• Load barrel in Garbage Truck and spin dial to “unload” it out the back!
• Includes Garbage Truck, The Joker figure and 3 barrels

This product is sold exclusively at Toys R Us.

column6: BRB CR CR DL NRSE AA

column7: 6 sing-along nursery rhymes sung by one of baby’s favorite Laugh & Learn® characters, Sis!
column8:
It’s rhyme time! Nursery rhymes are music to little ones’ ears because the rhythm & repetition make them easy to remember. Turning the pages of this storybook introduces tots to favorites like “Pat-a-Cake” and “Row, Row, Row Your Boat” led by Sis. Or baby can press any of the 3 light-up buttons to discover letters, numbers, colors, fun surprises and more on each page. And when you gotta book, grab the top handle to keep baby entertained on the go-go-go!

• 6 sing-along nursery rhymes! -Itsy Bitsy Spider-Row, Row, Row Your Boat-One, Two, Buckle My Shoe-Animal Fair-Pat-a-Cake-Hickory Dickory Dock
• Features familiar favorite Laugh & Learn® character, Sis
• 3 light-up buttons teach counting, first words, letters, colors, shapes and more!
• Easy-to-turn pages help boost fine motor skills
• Top handle makes it easy to take on the go-go-go!

This product is sold exclusively at Toys R Us.

column8:

Explore el verano with Dora! She’s dressed for a sunny adventure in a blue-and-white striped dress and pretty summertime sandals.

Features
• Stands approximately 8’’ tall and features poseable arms and legs.
• Features soft hair little girls will love to brush and style.

Join Dora for a gymnastics adventure!

Dora is ready to wow the crowd with her big gymnastics routine! Fisher-Price® Dora and Friends™ Gymnast Dora comes with a pink leotard and a medal she can wear.

Features
• Stands approximately 8’’ tall and features poseable arms and legs
• Includes a gymnastics medal

column6: Dora and Friends™ Color Surprise Bath Time Dora
column8:
Make bath time a color adventure with Dora!

This beautiful bath time Dora doll features a pretty ponytail with a fun color-change surprise! Use warm water to magically change the highlight in Dora’s hair from purple to pink! ¡Fantástico!

Features
• 8’’ Dora doll features a color-change hair highlight!
• Warm water magically changes Dora’s ponytail highlight from purple to pink!

Get ready for rescues with Dashi and the slime-shooting Gup-X!

It’s slime time! The tough Gup-X always gets Octonauts where they need to go–even if that means getting out of some pretty sticky situations! Dashi can activate the sea slime shooter to dispense the slime dart or deploy the Octo-Ski for short, scouting missions and sneaking through small spaces! Perfect for both land and bath missions, this slime-shooting Gup-X makes a great addition to your Gup fleet! Includes the Gup-X, Dashi, slime dart and a coconut crab to rescue!

Features
• No mission is impossible when you have the Gup-X!
• Features a sea slime shooter that launches a slime dart!
• Press the button to launch the Octo-Ski! It’s the perfect vehicle to reach and rescue the coconut crab!
• The Gup-X comes with Dashi, a slime dart and a coconut crab figure

column6: Blaze and the Monster Machines™ Firefighting Blaze
column8:
Fire truck Blaze with pivoting spring-loaded water cannon and flaming flip-down targets!

Blaze is ready to join all of his big-wheeled buddies on a new high-octane adventure! This time there's a fire, so Blaze has transformed into a water-blasting rescue vehicle, just like he does on the show. Aim and fire Blaze's spring-loaded water cannon to shoot water projectiles at the flaming flip-down targets. This small-scale fire truck Blaze with pivoting water cannon and spring-loaded launcher includes everything you need to recreate an exciting new adventure of Blaze and the Monster Machines™!

Features
• Fire truck Blaze
• Pivoting water cannon launches projectiles
• Flip down flame targets

column6: Blaze and the Monster Machines™ Zeg Pit Area
column8:
Smash and bash vehicle playset with a pivoting launcher that sends Zeg crashing through three different smash-up targets!

Zeg is ready to smash, crash, and knock over his targets in this new action-filled playset from Blaze and the Monster Machines™. Slam and launch Zeg in one of three directions: smash through a wall, knock over a crossbones target, and topple a tree to reveal hidden fossils! Set Zeg in the pivoting launcher and point it to one of the three target areas of impact. Slam down on the launcher and send Zeg flying into the air. Each target gets knocked over as Zeg comes crashing through! Slam & Crash Zeg can be played with alone or can connect to the Monster Dome Playset (sold separately and subject to availability), and includes an additional curved track piece for more fun and layout possibilities. Expand the world of Axle City with this fun new Slam & Crash Zeg playset.

Features
• Smashing & bashing action
• Slam & launch Zeg 3 ways
• Aim Zeg at 3 different targets
• Connects to other track sets (sold separately and subject to availability)
• Zeg’s big smashing and bashing action helps kids explore mass!

Thomas & Friends™ Pullback Toy Train for Toddlers with Puffing Steam Cloud

It’s time to race full steam ahead with Pullback Puffers from Fisher-Price! Pull Thomas back and watch his steam cloud puff up and down while he speeds along. Children will experience fun-filled, beneficial play as they use fine motor skills to grasp the toy and pull it back. Pullback Puffers can also help inspire imaginations as toddlers create their own adventures for their favorite characters. Get ready for a rolling, steam-puffing journey with this adorable collection of Thomas & Friends™ engines!

Features
• Pull Thomas back, then release him to watch him race along
• As he rolls, his steam cloud moves up and down
• Perfect introduction to Thomas & Friends™, or great addition to your child’s collection of toy trains
• Collect your favorite Thomas & Friends™ characters as Pullback Puffers (sold separately and subject to availability)

column6: My First Thomas & Friends™ Thomas Rail Rumbler
column8:
Thomas & Friends™ Soft Vibrating Plush Toys for Toddlers

Get ready for rolling, rumbling railway adventures with Rail Rumblers from
Fisher-Price! Children will love playing with these uniquely soft and squeezable versions of their favorite Thomas & Friends™ characters. Just pull their steam clouds and watch these adorable engines rumble and shake. With engines numbered one through six in a variety of different colors, Rail Rumblers can put little engineers on track to recognizing colors and numbers. The colors, textures, and unique movements also deliver an engaging sensory experience that will keep children giddy and giggling as they watch their favorite Thomas & Friends™ characters rumble along!

Features
• Round, soft plush versions of your favorite Thomas & Friends™ characters
• Pull their steam clouds for rumbling action
• Collect your favorite Thomas & Friends™ characters designed with their engine color and number (sold separately and subject to availability)

Rev up Blaze and his friends for some messy monster truck excitement! This special 3-pack of Blaze and the Monster Machines™ vehicles features three Monster Machine vehicles with an entirely unique styling, this time featuring the muddier side of monster truck racing. Blaze and his buddies are covered in mud from a full day of racing and fun. Now you can collect all 3 specially designed trucks all at once with this collector 3-pack, sold exclusively at Target.

• Sold exclusively at Target.

Blaze and his buddies are decorated in black with glossy trim for some far-out racing fun. column6: HW MJ EL TORO LOCO BLACK
SHIMMER & SHINE MAGICAL GENIE WISH PENDANT
Disney Princess Rapunzel's Tower by Little People®
column7: Recreate the Rapunzel fairy tale with this magical tower playset, featuring climbing basket with trap door, “hair” elevator and rocking boat.
column8:
Rapunzel has let her hair down (literally)! Now it’s up to little Disney Princess fans to decide the rest of the story. Will they let Flynn Rider “climb” Rapunzel’s locks to rescue her from the tower to live happily ever after? Or will they press the basket to send him flying through the trap door before he can reach his princess? (Don’t worry, he’s okay – just open the front door of the tower playset to retrieve him for the next hair-raising adventure!) To help Rapunzel & Flynn make a fast getaway, put them in the boat and rock it back & forth to “row” away. Little ones can use their greatest magical power – imagination – to reenact the classic fairy tale or restyle the story their way.

• Going up! “Hair” basket moves up & down to “climb” tower
• Look out below! Press basket to open the trap door & send figure tumbling down
• Open the front door to see who fell through the trap door
• It’s okay to rock the boat – just tip it back & forth for peek-a-boo fun!
• Includes Rapunzel’s Tower playset and Rapunzel & Flynn Rider figures
• Little People® figures are sized just right for kid-sized hands

column7: Crawling action, upbeat music and a rotating mane encourage baby to crawl along with lion!
column8:
Ready, set, crawl! This adorable plush first friend for baby is “roaring” to go, go, go! Baby’s gentle touch sets lion in motion – moving back and forth & side to side with lively music that encourages baby to crawl along, too!

• A gentle press on the lion’s back activates motorized crawling motion and fun music to help get baby crawling, too!
• Encourages development of motor skills, balance and coordination
• Music, movement and plush texture help stimulate baby’s senses
• Baby’s actions makes fun things happen, teaching about cause & effect

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Sweet Cherry Minnie
column8:
5-inch cherry-scented Minnie dress-up doll that comes with a snap-on dress, bow and shoes.

Minnie Mouse is a sweet dream in her cherry inspired easy snap-on dress! Minnie’s outfit comes with a lovely cherry-colored bow, cupcake sprinkle dress and sweet snap-on shoes. But not only does Minnie look sweet – she smells sweet as well! Includes a 5-inch cherry-scented Minnie dress-up doll, snap-on dress, bow and shoes.

Features
• Includes 5-inch cherry-scented Minnie dress-up doll
• Easy snap-on dress, bow and shoes

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Sugar Sweet Styles
column8:
Vanilla-scented Minnie figure that comes with 3 complete outfits with 15 sweet fashion pieces.

Minnie Mouse is ready to add some sweetly inspired fashions to her already sweet wardrobe! This style-filled fashion accessory set comes with 3 complete outfits with 15 fashion pieces in a whole new sweet fashion theme. In fact, Minnie has so many fashions to choose from you can mix and match the accessories for dozens of sweet looks only you can create! This fashion and accessory set comes with a 5-inch vanilla-scented Minnie figure and 3 complete outfits in three different sugar sweet styles: sweet candy, yummy ice cream, and luscious cupcake. Includes dresses, shoes, bows, and lots of fun accessories. Everything Minnie needs for some super sweet vanilla-scented fun!

Features
• 5-inch vanilla-scented Minnie figure
• 3 different fashions
• Easy snap-on outfits & accessories
• 15 fashion pieces in all

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Sundae Treats Stand
column8:
Complete Minnie’s shopping world with this fun figure pack set that goes along with Minnie’s Fabulous Shopping Mall.

Let’s have a sweet treat while shopping at the Fabulous Shopping Mall! After a day of shopping, Minnie Mouse serves up a frozen treat at her Sundae Treats Stand. Dressed in her super cute ice cream outfit, Minnie serves some refreshing ice cream sundaes to her friends. This 3-inch Minnie figure comes with an ice cream tray and frozen treat cart with umbrella! (Fabulous Shopping Mall sold separately and subject to availability.)

Features
• 3-inch Minnie figure
• Includes frozen treats stand
• 3 play pieces in all

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Mall Makeover Stand
column8:
Complete Minnie’s shopping world with this fun figure pack set that goes along with Minnie’s Fabulous Shopping Mall.

Everyone loves getting all made up while shopping at the Fabulous Shopping Mall, so it’s time for a makeover with Daisy Duck at her Mall Makeover Stand. Have a seat in the makeup chair and get glamorized at the vanity table. When Daisy has finished applying her makeup, check out the final look in the pretend mirror. Includes 3-inch Daisy figure, chair, makeup kit and counter. (Fabulous Shopping Mall sold separately and subject to availability.)

Features
• 3-inch Daisy figure
• Includes makeup table
• 3 play pieces in all

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Fashion Photo Fun
column8:
Fun figure and accessory set that features a 3-inch Minnie figure and 9 stylish accessory pieces, including a magic-reveal photo booth.

Complete your day at Minnie Mouse’s Fabulous Shopping Mall with this Fashion Photo Fun figure and accessory set. Minnie’s been shopping all day, and now it’s time to take everything she’s bought and dress her up for a glamorous photo shoot. Shop at the different stands and kiosks before sitting Minnie in the makeup chair and glamming her up. Have Minnie step in front of the scenic background or into the magic-reveal photo booth to take some fun selfies! Slide the curtain on the photo booth to reveal some of Minnie’s best glam shots. Comes with camera and photographer’s light; chair and jewelry kiosk; sunglasses stand and two shopping kiosks; and a 2-sided backdrop for taking professional photos. Everything you need to make your mall adventure fabulous fun! (Fabulous Shopping Mall sold separately and subject to availability.)

Features
• 3-inch Minnie figure
• Magic-reveal photo booth
• 9 fun accessory pieces in all

column6: Disney Minnie Mouse – Splash ’n Spin Daisy
column8:
Fun bathtime Daisy figure that spins in the water as she raises her arms up over her head in a pretty ballet pose.

Daisy figure dressed in a pretty water-dancing outfit. Move Daisy’s arms up and down to wind her up and watch her spin in the water in a pretty dance pose. The more you push her arms, the faster she twirls! Apply warm water to Daisy’s dress to make the flowers on her dress magically change color. Also includes a cute flower-shaped water strainer for more bathtime fun. Also available: Splash ‘n Spin Minnie - sold separately and subject to availability.

Features
• Wind-up Daisy figure bath toy
• 6-inch Daisy spins & twirls
• Magical color change dress
• Strainer for more fun in the tub

column7: Imaginext® collectible figures make the action happen!
column8:
In the Imaginext® worlds, these are more than just figures. They’re characters who can literally make an action happen, just by placing them on any Power Pad in any Imaginext® play set and giving it a press or a turn! Integrating characters into the action really enhances imaginative play.

So do the cool accessories that come with each action figure! Collect all the Imaginext® Series 6 Collectible Figures: jester, dino mech, female pilot, chicken suit, alien and gnome. (Each sold separately and subject to availability.) Imaginext®…Turn on Adventure!™

• Each blind foil pack contains one collectible figure and cool accessories
• Integrating these action figures into any Imaginext® play set really enhances imaginative play
• Collect all Series 6 figures: jester, dino mech, female pilot, chicken suit, alien and gnome. (Each sold separately and subject to availability.)

Disney Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates - Captain Jake
column8:
Fun poseable 3-inch Captain Jake collectible character figure.

Jake has been promoted to Captain Jake, and he’s ready for some all new adventures on the seas of Never Land. This fun affordable 3-inch character figure helps you to pretend that you’re part of the pirate action on the Never Sea. As always, Jake is ready to take on the unflappable Captain Hook, but be on the lookout because Jake also has a new nemesis, the slithery Lord Fathom. He’s going to need some help from his trusty pirate pals, and he needs you to come along for the journey. Assortment of three poseable 3-inch character figures: Captain Jake, Captain Hook, and Lord Fathom – each sold separately and subject to availability.

Features
• Poseable 3-inch Jake, Hook, & Lord Fathom figures
• Collect them all!
• Each sold separately and subject to availability

column8:
Fun poseable 3-inch Captain Hook collectible figure.

Captain Hook is always itchin’ for a battle with his arch-nemesis Jake, but things have gotten even tougher ever since Jake was promoted to Captain Jake! Styled in a new pose and outfit, this fun affordable 3-inch character figure helps you to pretend that you’re part of the pirate action on the Never Sea. As always, Captain Hook is ready to take on the unflappable Captain Jake, but be on the lookout because there’s also a new enemy to keep an eye out for: the slithery Lord Fathom. column6: Disney Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates - Key to the Sea Battle Adventure
column8:
Captain Jake’s trusty skiff is newly equipped with a secret skull key feature that can only be unlocked by whoever possesses the golden key.

Now that Jake’s been promoted to Captain he’s ready to set sail on a whole new adventure, so he needs a brand new skiff. Captain Jake’s trusty new skiff has been equipped with a new secret skull key feature that can only be unlocked by the person who possesses the secret golden skull key. With his new skeleton key in hand, Captain Jake can turn the main sail of his ship and unlock a new secret adventure. X unlocks the spot as you insert the key into the top of Bucky’s crow’s nest and twist. As you turn the key, the mast pivots and unlocks the secret plank that slides out, revealing Captain Jake’s hidden treasure. But what if the ship comes under attack by Captain Hook? Captain Jake’s new battle ship also comes equipped with a cannon that launches anchor-shaped projectiles to keep the pirate baddies at bay. You’ll control the key to the sea as you use the secret golden key to unlock Captain Jake’s newest pirate adventure. Discover the powers of your imagination and creativity as you’re transported to the world of Captain Jake and the Never Land Pirates!

Features
• Skeleton key unlocks secret play feature
• Cannon launches anchor-shaped projectiles
• Includes 3-inch poseable Captain Jake figure

©Disney
