column6: Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Silly Grillin' Mickey
column8:
A camping-themed figure set that comes with a Mickey Mouse figure and Pluto figure sitting around the campfire and roasting a hot dog on a rotating Mouska-hands rotisserie!

It’s time for some fun around the campfire with Mickey Mouse and his clubhouse pal, Pluto! Mickey and Pluto love grilling outdoors with their special Mouska-hands rotisserie grill. Help Mickey turn the crank to rotate and cook the hot dog - just make sure Pluto doesn’t get to it before Mickey does! This figure set comes with a poseable Mickey figure and Pluto figure along with Mickey’s Mouska-hands holding the rotating grill over the open campfire- 3 fun camping pieces in all. It’s a fun and silly cooking adventure that you and Mickey can have together while enjoying the great outdoors! Also available: Silly Grillin’ Donald - sold separately and subject to availability.

Features
• Includes 3-inch poseable Mickey figure
• Pluto figure & rotating rotisserie grill
• 3 fun pieces in all

column6: Disney Mickey Mouse Clubhouse - Silly Grillin' Donald
column8:
A camping-themed figure set that comes with a Donald Duck figure and Chip ‘n Dale figure sitting around the campfire and frying up a fresh fish dinner!

It’s time for some fun around the campfire with Donald Duck and his clubhouse pals, Chip ‘n Dale! Donald loves grilling outdoors, and he’s been out all day fishing, so he has quite a catch that he has to grill up on the open campfire. Help Donald fry up some fish by flipping the frying pan to see the fresh fish turn into a delicious fish-fry dinner! Just make sure that Chip ‘n Dale don’t eat it all before Donald does! This figure set comes with a poseable Donald figure and a Chip ‘n Dale figure along with a flip-action frying pan sitting atop the open campfire- 3 fun camping pieces in all. It’s a fun and silly cooking adventure that you and Donald can have together while enjoying the great outdoors! Also available: Silly Grillin’ Mickey - sold separately and subject to availability.

Features
• Includes 3-inch poseable Donald Duck figure
• Chip ‘n Dale figure & flip-action frying pan
• 3 fun pieces in all

column7: Activities all around with balls, blocks & pegs to roll, stack & place! Music, lights & spinnin’ action, too!
column8:
Reserve the best table in town for your favorite wee one! At the Silly Safari Musical Activity Table, baby will discover hands-on activities at every turn. Like blocks to stack. Balls to roll. Sweet animal friends to peg. A big button to push for lights, music & cup-spinning action. A book to flip. A teeter-totter to rock. And a piano to play!

Attach the legs to have the activity table “grow” with your little one, from sitting to standing play. Lots of activities, lots of music & lights and lots of action encourage baby to move and explore all around the table – helping to give your little one’s gross motor skills a big boost!

• Musical Activity Table combines ball, block & peg fun with music, lights and spinning action!
• Stack blocks in center for music & light rewards
• Push button to spin cups, make the middle light up & music play
• Put balls or pegs in cups to take them for a ride!
• Place animal pegs in hole to hear silly sounds!
• Press piano keys to play notes & activate lights!
• Flip book, roller ball and teeter-totter for baby to explore
• Includes 2 animal pegs, 2 blocks & 2 balls
• Legs easily attach for grow-with-me play
• Boost happy, skill-building play with busy activities & all-around exploration
• Lights, music, sounds & movement help stimulate important senses

column7: A new spin on drop-through ball play with musical rewards, ramp-riding action & a surprise finish!
column8:
Go ahead…give this fun musical toy a whirl! Baby can get the ball rolling by dropping one of the 4 balls through the elephant’s trunk to hear fun tunes and watch it come swirlin’ and twirlin’ down the ramp. Or your little one can cruise around this elephant pal and drop balls anywhere on the wrap-around ramp – and chase after when the balls roll out the bottom in every direction!

Baby will love collecting the balls and dropping them on the ramp again…and again…and again! There’s even a snail to slide and a roller bar to bat at. The Silly Safari Swirlin’ Surprise Elephant offers all-around, fine-motor activity fun and easy clean-up with corners in the sturdy base to store the balls.

• 2 ways to play!
• Drop balls through the elephant’s trunk to activate fun tunes & ramp-rolling action!
• Or drop balls directly on the wrap-around ramp for whirlin’, twirlin’, swirlin’ fun!
• Balls roll out bottom for baby to chase, collect & drop through again (and again and again!)
• Where will the balls come out? It’s a surprise every time!
• Slider snail & bat-at roller bar provide more hands-on activities
• Includes 4 balls and 10 tunes
• Sturdy base with corners to store the balls
• Helps give motor skills a fun workout!
• Music and action help stimulate important senses, including vision and hearing

column7: Go out on a limb for baby with lots of fun activities, drop-through play & musical rewards!
column8:
All the fun of a real treehouse…now you can take it inside for baby with this musical activity toy! 2 adorable Peg Pals are just the right size for small hands to grasp & hold – and drop through the treetop over and over (and over!) again. Tots are rewarded with a fun little ditty when they lift the leaf to drop their pals! And peek-a-boo…open the door at the bottom of the treehouse to see their buddies “magically” reappear! There’s a butterfly to press for lights and music, a roller to spin, a lion window for peek-a-boo play and an adorable birdie that goes “click, click” instead of “tweet, tweet.” With the Silly Safari Musical Discovery Treehouse, baby is rewarded with fun sounds, lights and music as they discover & play – teaching cause & effect all along the way.

• Lift leaf in treetop to activate music and drop the animal Peg Pals!
• Open door at bottom of treehouse to bring friends out to play again!
• Press butterfly for lights & music!
• Roller bar, peek-a-boo lion window and clicker bird provide more hands-on fun!
• Peg Pals are the perfect size for little hands to hold
• Helps give fine motor skills a boost
• Baby’s actions make fun things happen – a great introduction to cause & effect!

column7: This croc’s chock full of blocks, with toggling action to get baby crawling after!
column8:
This silly croc activity toy includes 3 Stackin’ Sensory Blocks with lots of textures, animal friends and colors for baby to explore. Your little one can stack the blocks or place them on platforms on the croc’s back. And that’s when the fun really gets rolling with this activity toy! As baby pushes the croc along, the first two platforms toggle up and down for exciting pop-up action – and the third platform spins around!

When this croc’s a rockin’, baby can’t help but crawl along, too! And we’ve saved more fun for the tail end – this croc’s tail “clicks” for even more fine motor and sensory stimulation!

• Cute croc with fun togglin’, spinnin’ block action that encourages baby to crawl after!
• Includes 3 Stackin’ Sensory Blocks with lots of textures, animal friends & colors to explore
• Baby can stack blocks or place them on platforms on croc’s back
• First 2 platforms pop up and down; 3rd platform spins around
• Clicker tail
• Gives a big boost to fine and gross motor skills
• Bright colors and fun motions grab baby’s attention and help develop all-important senses

column7: 4 colorful characters are ready to make some noise for baby with their own unique sounds!
column8:
Rattle! Click! Squeak! Ding! Shake ’em baby and see how these 4 adorable animal toys sound off for you! With just a shake, twist or push, your little one is rewarded with a unique sound from each character. The croc is a clicker, the tiger is a squeaker, the hippo is a bell and the lion is a rattle. And these noisemakers all have something special to add to baby’s fine motor skill building and sensory stimulation.

We’ve made them to fit perfectly in baby-sized hands, and peg into other Fisher-Price Silly Safari toys like the Musical Activity Table and Musical Discovery Treehouse. (Sold separately and subject to availability.)

• 4 adorable pegged animal toys with their own unique sound!
• Includes clicking croc, squeaking tiger, chiming hippo and rattling lion
• Perfectly sized for little hands to grasp & hold
• Give baby’s fine motor skills a fun workout
• Bright colors and fun noises help stimulate important senses like sight & hearing!

column7: Shake, rattle and roll! Baby will love discovering what’s inside these roll-around activity balls!
column8:
These 6 animal friend activity toys are just the right size for little hands to shake & roll around, and they reward your little one’s actions with a flip, a flutter or a rattle sound! What’s that you hear? It’s your tot’s senses and motor skills being stimulated in a wildly fun way with these adorable balls!

• 6 animal rounds with flippers, flutters & rattle beads inside for baby to discover!
• Baby-sized activity toys for baby-sized hands
• Adorable animal characters
• Bright colors & fun sounds grab baby’s attention and help stimulate developing senses
• Baby’s actions make fun things happen, introducing cause & effect

column7: We give building blocks a fun twist with sounds, flippers, rollers, mirrors and touchy-feely textures!
column8:
Flip, roll, squeak…rattle, feel, peek! These are the new building blocks of fun for your busy little one. Six character blocks feature lots for babies to see & do, stimulating their senses and helping them “build” fine motor skills too! And we’ve done some nifty construction of our own, making these toy blocks the perfect size for little hands to grasp, shake, stack & roll!

• 6 colorful character toy blocks for baby to hold, stack & roll
• Each block has a fun feature: a flipper, roller, squeaker, rattle beads, mirror and touchy-feely textures!
• Perfect for baby-sized hands to grasp
• Stack up wonderfully for helping to build fine motor skills
• The bright colors, fun textures & sounds help stimulate baby’s senses of sight, hearing & touch!

column7: Give these fun characters a spin, with gravity-defying action to amaze little ones!
column8:
What are YOs and what makes them go? They’re cool, round things that love to spin fast, and love to spin slow. “How do they stay on track?” kids ask as they play. It’s ’magic’ of course! (That’s what you should say.) Just place one or both YOs on the track piece. Then take the YOs for a ride…make ’em slide … go upside down … and ’round & ’round & ’round! It’s a whole new spin on defying gravity! There’s a crazy character on one side of each YO, and a cool visual effect on the other side. The track piece easily attaches to sections of the Spinnyos™ Giant YO-ller Coaster™ set for more spin-tacular fun! (Coaster sold separately.)

How do YOs stay on the track? Well, it seems like magic, but actually there’s a kid-safe magnetic axle inside the YOs spinners that attaches to the metallic edge on the track. They’re so much fun that once kids start spinning ’em, they won’t want to stop! (You won’t either – try ’em and see for yourself!) They’re YO-tally awesome!

• Place the Spinnyos™ YOs on the track piece and move it in any direction to send the YOs spinning up, down and all around!
• Wacky character on one side, cool visual effect on the other
• Each pack includes 2 YOs and 1 track piece that attaches to sections of the Spinnyos™ Giant YO-ller Coaster™ set (sold separately)
• Discover the YO-tally wacky world of Spinnyos™ spinners! Collect all the YOs in different fun themes! (Each sold separately and subject to availability)
• Perfect toy for on-the-go play!

column7: This Batcave play set has cool gadgets for protecting Gotham City, including a robot suit with interchangeable arm pieces!
column8:
The usual suspects are stirring up trouble in Gotham City. To the Robo Batcave, Batman™! Turn the 1st Power Pad to open the gate, raise the Bat-shaped head and reveal the Batbot. (The Batman™ figure fits inside!) Turn the 2nd Power Pad on the bottom of the play set to move the Batbot forward and march him into any crime-fighting adventure young wannabe DC Super Heroes can think up!

In an all-out battle with Gotham City villains? Just turn the 3rd Power Pad to swing the Batbot’s arm that can be fitted with a claw, jaws of life or Gatling gun accessory. And if the Robo Batcave comes under attack, push the button to fire the projectile launcher or throw captured villains in jail. There’s no end to the adventures when kids use their greatest super power – imagination!

• Turn 1st Power Pad to open the Robo Batcave play set and reveal the Batbot
• Turn 2nd Power Pad to move Batbot forward and release it from the play set
• Turn 3rd Power Pad to swing the Batbot’s arm
• Fit any of 3 interchangeable accessories on the Batbot’s arm: claw, jaws of life, or Gatling gun
• Place Batman™ figure in Batbot suit to lead the battle!
• Robo Batcave play set also features projectile launcher and jail cell
• Includes Robo Batcave, Batbot, Batman™ figure & 2 projectiles

column7: The ultra-lite, portable play yard that weighs just 15 lbs.!
column8:
Take some weight off your shoulders with a portable play yard that’s just half the weight of other popular play yards, with all the same great features, and more.It’s everything you and baby need to play, sleep, change and repeat —at home or on the go! At only 15 lbs., it’s super lightweight and easy-peasy to pop up, take down and pack away in just a few quick, simple steps.

A supportive seat back, with plush head support, cozy insert and a three point restraint help keep baby comfy in the inclined sleeper – the way lots of babies sleep best. Remove the sleeper and it becomes a roomy space for older babies and toddlers to rest, relax and play. Too-good-to-be-true details include a padded mattress that fits any standard-size play yard sheet and a built-in play yard storage pocket that holds a portable changing station diaper clutch—great for quick and easy diaper changes at home, or on the go. Plenty of room to BYO diapers! The Ultra-Lite Day & Night Play Yard is a night saver – and a life saver.

• Easy to assemble
• Easy to fold—no loose pieces

Wooden Toys Rhythm & Roll Percussion Plane
column7: Rolling Musical Toy Airplane for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!
column8:
Airplanes are usually powered by propellers or jet engines, but the Rhythm & Roll Percussion Plane from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys is powered by creativity, imagination, and your child’s budding motor skills. Made with real beech wood, this artfully crafted toy airplane encourages toddlers to make their own fly beats using the güiro—the hollow gourd-like percussion instrument on top of the plane—and the propeller cymbals.

Of course, they can also use their motor skills to roll the plane along, and their imaginations to pretend it’s flying through the air. Children’s self-expression and creativity will soar to new heights as they create their own rhythm for the soundtrack of their early development.

• Rolling toy airplane is made with real beech wood
• Remove the stick from the plane’s tail to play the guiro
• Children can use the stick or their fingers to play the cymbal propellers
• Grasping the plane, rolling it along, and picking it up to “fly” it through the air promotes fine and gross motor skills
• Making sounds using the güiro and cymbals helps inspire imagination, creativity, and self-expression
• Playing the güiro and cymbals provides visual, auditory, and tactile stimulation

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column6: Wooden Toys Sweet Sounds Ice Cream Truck
column7: Rolling Musical Toy Truck Made with Real Wood!
column8:
Since the 1920s, ice cream trucks have filled the air with sweet, familiar melodies. From local neighborhoods to beaches and parks, these musical vehicles offer more than sugary treats—they deliver the sounds of summer. Now children can create their own musical melodies with the Sweet Sounds Ice Cream Truck from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys, an heirloom-quality toy truck delivering fun-filled play that can help promote early childhood development. As children use the mallet to play the chimes, they’re exercising fine motor skills and imagination while expressing themselves creatively. Ringing the bell also promotes curiosity and logical thinking as they discover what mechanisms produce fun, exciting sounds.

Plus, pushing and rolling the truck along can also help encourage gross motor skills through physical play. This musical vehicle is meticulously constructed using real beech wood and stylishly designed to offer a stimulating sensory experience with engaging colors, appealing textures, and charming sounds. Explore the endless potential of a child’s imagination, and share the musical journey with the Sweet Sounds Ice Cream Truck from Fisher-Price.

• Rolling musical ice cream truck is made with real beech wood
• Includes chimes on the side, bell on top, and a mallet to play the chimes
• Grasping the Ice Cream Truck promotes eye-hand coordination and finger dexterity
• Rolling the truck along encourages physical activity and gross motor skills
• Making sounds and melodies using the chimes and bell helps inspire imagination, creativity, and self-expression
• Playing the chimes and ringing the bell provides visual, auditory, and tactile stimulation
• Ringing the bell fosters curiosity and encourages exploration about how things work

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column7: Octopus Toy for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood
column8:
What has eight arms, lives in the ocean, and loves to party? The Sea Party Octopus, of course! But this unique octopus, from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys, doesn’t want to celebrate alone, so he’s looking for some fishy friends to join the festivities. Children can use fine motor skills along with thinking and problem solving as they discover how to pick up the fish with the octopus’ tentacles. When toddlers help this social sea creature meet some new companions, they’ll feel like the life of the sea party!

• Includes toy octopus and two fish made with real beech wood
• Fish can be “caught” and picked up using the octopus’ tentacles
• Fine motor skills are encouraged as children use eye-hand coordination to grasp the octopus and pick up the fish with his tentacles
• Discovering how to pick up the fish fosters logical thinking and problem solving

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column7: Designed to help children develop through fun, beneficial play, this unique set of wooden toys and accessories lets toddlers mix, match, stack, and create their own original totem towers.
column8:
Totem poles are sculptures carved on tall, wooden posts, some of which can reach over sixty feet (18 meters) tall. Although toddlers may not be able to stack these wooden toys quite so high, they’ll love using fine motor skills to connect them, and imagination and creativity to rearrange their unique accessories. These artfully crafted Totem Pole Pals, from the Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys collection, are made with real beech wood and designed to be equally beneficial, eye-catching, and engaging.

Each wooden piece features different faces and expressions, along with bristles that allow for easy connection to the other pieces in the set. Plus, the circular faces can rotate between the bristles, so toddlers can spin them to see the varying expressions. As children build their totem towers, they can use the adorable, interchangeable accessories to customize them. With fun decorations like a hat, moustache, bowtie, lips, glasses and bunny ears, toddlers can create original combinations that reflect a variety of characteristics, personalities, emotions, and expressions. As children stack them up, up, up, their smiles will grow, grow, grow. You can even call these tactical totems “mood elevators.” (See what we did there?)

• Set includes 7 accessories and 6 wooden pieces decorated with unique facial expressions
• Pegs make pieces easily connectable and stackable
• Grasping the pieces and putting them together can encourage fine motor skills
• Figuring out how to connect and stack the pieces can foster logical thinking and problem solving
• Using the pieces and accessories to build unique totem towers can inspire imagination and creativity
• The different colors and textures provide a stimulating visual and tactile playtime experience

column6: Wooden Toys Deep Blue Sea Stacker
column7: Designed to foster physical and cognitive development in toddlers, this unique stacking toy features lights, sounds, and games that are meant to encourage fine motor skills, logical thinking, problem solving, curiosity, and discovery.
column8:
They say there are plenty of fish in the sea—and they’re right! But there are also plenty of crabs, turtles, snails, and other critters that live beneath the waves. At Fisher-Price®, we like to imagine these sea-dwellers do a lot of socializing—parties, line dancing, barbecues, and, of course, games. (Okay, maybe not too many barbecues.) The Deep Blue Sea Stacker, from the Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys collection, lets children take part in a variety of games featuring nine adorable play pieces designed to look like different underwater animals. With lights, sounds, and four modes of play, the Deep Blue Sea Stacker is more than a stacking toy; it’s an interactive playtime experience created to help foster physical and cognitive development. Each mode focuses on a different way to play by encouraging recognition of colors, shapes, and numbers through matching, stacking, and counting as children place the play pieces on the correct poles. To make sure children receive plenty of visual, auditory, and tactile stimulation, the toy features lots of music, sound effects, colored lights, and a gorgeous beech wood design to tie it all together. Contemporary meets classic with tried-and-true developmental play (stacking and matching), a modern aesthetic, and unique, fun-filled electronic content that helps guide children through different games, all of which are meant to encourage fine motor skills, logical thinking, problem solving, curiosity, and discovery. Deep sea adventures have never been more accessible. Whether your child is an aspiring oceanographer, or just loves playing with lights, sounds, and adorable animals, the Deep Blue Sea Stacker brings a world of fun, beneficial play to the surface.

• Unique sea-inspired stacking toy is made with real beech wood
• Includes 9 play pieces designed to look like a variety of sea creatures
• Stack the sea creatures by placing them on the correct poles
• The shapes of the sea creatures correspond to the shapes of the 3 different poles—circle, square, triangle
• 4 modes of play encourage recognition of shapes, colors, and numbers
• Different modes feature lights, sounds, phrases, and music
• Grasping and stacking the sea creatures helps promote fine motor skills
• Figuring out which sea creatures fit on which poles can foster logical thinking and problem solving
• Hearing the sound effects and seeing the lights as the creatures are stacked can inspire curiosity about how things work
• The variety of sights, sounds, and textures offers an array of visual, auditory, and tactile stimulation

column7: Café Role-play Set for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood
column8:
A hot cup of joe isn’t the only cure for a Case of the Mondays—the morning fog will melt away as you watch children serve up a dash of sugar, a dollop of milk, a scoop of self-expression, and a heaping spoonful of creativity. The Early Bird Barista Set from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys helps toddlers engage in fun-filled early role-play activities as they “make and serve” their coffee creations.

Featuring two coffee cups, a milk carton, sugar shaker, and a French press with plastic beans, this gorgeous café set, made with real beech wood, gives children a chance to craft a unique playtime experience filled with self-expression, creativity, and cooperation. After all, it’s easy to wake up on the right side of the bed when you know they’ll be laughing, sharing, and using their imaginations.

• Early role-play café set is made with real beech wood
• Set includes two coffee cups, milk carton, sugar shaker, and French press with plastic beans
• Engaging in early role-play activities helps promotes self-expression and confidence
• Using the set to play with other children encourages sharing and cooperation
• “Making and drinking” coffee creations helps inspire imagination and creativity

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column6: Wooden Toys Hungry Humpback Shape Sorter
column7: Whale Shape Sorter Toy for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!
column8:
Humpback whales usually only feed in summer, but this Hungry Humpback Shape Sorter from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys is eager to nosh all year round. Unlike other humpbacks, he won’t chase his food, so toddlers need to use fine motor skills along with thinking and problem solving to place those yummy shapes in his mouth. But he’s a picky eater, so if the shapes aren’t fed through the right openings, they may not end up in his big whale belly.

This set includes the adorably decorated whale shape sorter, made with real beech wood, along with three different shapes. The whale’s mouth can also open easily to access the shapes once they’ve been put inside. Children will love feeding this voracious, sea-dwelling mammal as they experience play that can help them develop physically and cognitively. So bon appétit, Hungry Humpback. Or, if you prefer, nom nom.

• Shape sorter set includes whale sorter and three different shapes
• Whale shape sorter and shapes are made with real beech wood
• Shapes can be placed into the openings of the whale’s mouth
• Top of the mouth can be opened for easy access to shapes, or closed for easy transport during on-the-go play
• Placing the shapes in the correct openings encourages logical thinking and problem solving
• Grasping the shapes and opening and closing the lid helps promote eye-hand coordination and fine motor skills
• The variety of colors and textures engages the senses with visual and tactile stimulation

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column7: Rolling Push Along Toy for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!
column8:
When a puppy’s coordination and strength improves, he begins to explore the world around him—and the Curious Pup from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys is ready to explore. He just needs a little push… literally. When children roll him along and watch his head wag back and forth, they’re using motor skills to engage in play that encourages their curiosity and imaginations.

Crafted from real beech wood and stylishly designed to engage the senses, this adorable push-along toy lets toddlers discover a new playtime companion. After all, a child’s youthful wonder helps lead to exploration and growth, just like a little puppy.

• Rolling toy puppy made from real beech wood
• When he’s pushed along, his head moves back and forth
• Grasping the puppy and rolling him along promotes fine and gross motor skills
• The colors and patterns help stimulate a child’s visual sense
• Seeing the puppy’s head move back and forth can help encourage curiosity about how things work

column7: Rolling Push Along Toy for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!
column8:
Alligators have strong jaws that help them chew and chomp. Fortunately, the Chomping Gator from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys isn’t fierce, he’s friendly, so toddlers can play all day without worrying about their little fingers and toes. When children roll this adorable baby reptile along, they’re helping him strengthen his young jaw. Of course, they’re also strengthening their own motor skills as they engage in play that helps stimulate their senses and their curiosity.

Made from real beech wood, this meticulously crafted, gorgeously designed push-along toy gator helps your child discover a new and unique playtime companion—without setting foot near a swamp.

Either way, when toddlers roll him along to watch him shiver and shake, they’re not just using motor skills to engage in fun-filled play, they’re offering a warm touch to a chilly bird.

column7: Give these fun characters a spin, with gravity-defying action to amaze little ones!
column8:
What are YOs and what makes them go? They’re cool, round things that love to spin fast, and love to spin slow. “How do they stay on track?” kids ask as they play. It’s ’magic’ of course! (That’s what you should say.) Just place one or both YOs on the track piece. Then take the YOs for a ride…make ’em slide…go upside down…and ’round & ’round & ’round! It’s a whole new spin on defying gravity! There’s a crazy character on one side of each YO, and a cool visual effect on the other side. The track piece easily attaches to sections of the Spinnyos™ Giant YO-ller Coaster™ set for more spin-tacular fun! (Coaster sold separately.)

How do YOs stay on the track? Well, it seems like magic, but actually there’s a kid-safe magnetic axle inside the YOs spinners that attaches to the metallic edge on the track. They’re so much fun that once kids start spinning ’em, they won’t want to stop! (You won’t either – try ’em and see for yourself!) They’re YO-tally awesome!

• Place the Spinnyos™ YOs on the track piece and move it in any direction to send the YOs spinning up, down and all around!
• Wacky character on one side, cool visual effect on the other
• Each pack includes 2 YOs and 1 track piece that attaches to sections of the Spinnyos™ Giant YO-ller Coaster™ set (sold separately)
• Discover the YO-tally wacky world of Spinnyos™ spinners! Collect all the YOs in different fun themes! (Each sold separately and subject to availability)
• Perfect toy for on-the-go play!

• Place the Spinnyos™ Fro-YOs on the YO-Rail™ track piece and move it in any direction to send the YOs spinning up, down and all around!
• Wacky frozen yogurt character on one side, cool visual effect on the other
• Includes 2 YOs and 1 YO-Rail™ track piece that attaches to the Spinnyos™ Giant YO-ller Coaster™ and H2YO Splash Park sets (sold separately)
• Discover the YO-tally wacky world of Spinnyos™ toys! Collect all the YOs in different fun themes! (Each sold separately and subject to availability)
• Perfect toy for on-the-go play!

column7: Puppy brings the magic of birthdays to life with a colorful, musical birthday cake!
column8:
Make a wish! Puppy and this colorful birthday cake bring early role play to life with shape-sorting fun, sounds, music, a magical light and more. Five colorful shapes numbered one through five decorate this playful cake. Ready to blow out the candle? A multi-color, light-up candle changes color to match the shapes as baby sorts them on the cake! Little hands can press the Puppy button to hear phrases, a brand new birthday song, and learn about shapes, colors and first words in Spanish.

Every baby develops at their own pace, and Smart Stages™ technology gives you the ability to select the stage that’s best for your child. There are a variety of developmentally appropriate songs, phrases and sounds within three levels of play – just slide the switch.

Smart Stages™ Technology
• Level 1 – Explore – 12M+. First words and sounds spark baby’s curiosity.
• Level 2 - Encourage – 18M+. Prompt baby through questions and simple directions.
• Level 3 – Pretend – 24M+. Imaginative fun and early role play.

Plus, the pieces are numbered one through five, so children can practice counting and number recognition as they stack their engine or match and connect the pieces.

column7: Shape-inspired Toy Turtle for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood
column8:
A turtle has the ability to hide his limbs and head when he’s scared, but your child can bring the Shape-imals™ Turtle out of his shell… literally. When children use their little fingers to open the turtle’s little arms and head, they’re engaging in play that promotes fine motor skills and fosters logical thinking and problem solving. Plus, the shape of this turtle’s circular beech wood body is no accident—the entire Shape-imals collection is designed to help encourage shape recognition. If only all geometry could be this adorable.

• Toy turtle with retractable head and arms is made with real beech wood
• When children open the head and arms from the body, it promotes fine motor skills along with logical thinking and problem solving
• Turtle’s circular body is designed to help encourage shape recognition

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

When toddlers help him spread his wings, they’re engaging in play that promotes fine motor skills and fosters logical thinking and problem solving. Plus, the shape of this owl’s triangular beech wood body is no accident—the entire Shape-imals™ collection is designed to help encourage shape recognition. If only all geometry could be this adorable.

• Toy owl with retractable wings is made with real beech wood

• Owl’s triangular body is designed to help encourage shape recognition

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column7: Shape-inspired Crab Toy for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!
column8:
Crabs have ten legs, the first being a pair of claws. But the Shape-imals™ Crab from Fisher-Price® Wooden Toys is a cheerful crustacean, so he won’t pinch your child’s fingers or toes. In fact, children are encouraged to use fine motor skills along with thinking and problem solving to open the crab’s eyes and claws, making him a full-fledged, pinch-free playtime companion. Plus, the diamond shape of this crab’s beech wood body is no accident—the entire Shape-imals™ collection is designed to help foster shape recognition. If only all geometry could be this adorable.

• Toy crab with retractable claws and eyes is made with real beech wood
• When children open the eyes and claws from the body, it promotes fine motor skills along with logical thinking and problem solving
• Crab’s diamond-shaped body is designed to help encourage shape recognition

This product is sold exclusively at Target.

column7: Shape-inspired Animal Toys for Toddlers Made with Real Beech Wood!

Plus, the shapes of these critters’ beech wood bodies resemble a triangle, circle, and diamond, respectively, because the entire Shape-imals™ collection is designed to help foster shape recognition. If only all geometry could be this adorable.

• Toy animals with retractable pieces made with real beech wood

column7: A soothing baby seat with bounce & sway motion!
column8:
Sweet serenity is closer than you think – with a soothing seat inspired by the natural motion of mom or dad. Customize the motion to whatever baby likes best. Bounce, sway or bounce and sway together, in the deep, cozy baby seat. Calming vibrations, 10 songs and 2 nature sounds add to the serene scene. The elevated frame design makes it easy-peasy to get baby in & out.

• Bounce & sway motion – almost like being in mom & dad’s arms
• Three soothing motions: Bounce, Sway, Bounce & Sway
• Overhead mobile with three toys & mirror – easily swings away to get baby in & out
• Two position seat recline for baby’s comfort
• 10 songs & 2 nature sounds
• Soft & cozy, machine washable seat pad with infant insert & head support
• Sleek frame design takes up less space
• Includes AC adaptor for plug-in power
• Switch on calming vibrations

Developmental guidelines: Use from birth until child is able to sit up unassisted.

column7: Packed with more than 40 flaps, Little People™ Let’s Go to the Zoo!
column8:
takes kids on a learning adventure. Eddie, Sarah Lynn, and their friends discover colors, animal sounds, counting and more as they enjoy a trip to the town zoo. With so much to discover, this book will be one kids will want to open again and again!

For more information, please contact Reader’s Digest at 1-800-310-2181.

A fun triangular acetate tube holds 3 cute board books, a double-sided write-on, wipe-off playmat, 3 crayons, and stickers for lots of take-along farm fun.

For more information, please contact Reader’s Digest at 1-800-310-2181.

column6: Little People® Big Adventure Wood Puzzle-Castle
column8:
The series of 12 piece wood puzzles features Fisher-Price® Little People® in four adventure themes; Pet Shop, Dinosaur Cove, Pirate Ship and Castle. Each puzzle contains 12 large, easy to grasp wooden pieces. Wooden storage tray makes cleanup after play, easy and fun.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® Mix & Match Wood Puzzle-Eddie
column8:
Mix and Match different outfits with Eddie. What outfit will Eddie™ wear today? Each set includes 12 pieces: 5 tops, 5 bottoms and 2 different faces to create lots of unique and silly dress-up looks. Everything fits inside in a wooden box for easy cleanup and storage.

Each puzzle develops Imagination, self-expression and gross motor skills.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® All Aboard Numbers Learning Train
column8:
This colorful train puzzle is over 3 feet long and includes 30 extra large pieces. Colorful circus animals help young puzzlers learn to count from 1-10.

Each puzzle develops number recognition, fine motor skills and problem solving.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® World of Wheelies™  Activity Floor Puzzle-Farm
column7: Puzzles and vehicles combine to create a new world of fun.
column8:
Zoom your Little People® Wheelies™ vehicles over the completed floor puzzle. Each of the puzzles comes with its own unique vehicle, has 24 extra large pieces and is over two feet tall! Collect all 3 puzzles to create your one gigantic Wheelies world!

Farm floor puzzle includes Tractor.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® Discover & Learn Chunky Wood Puzzle-Farm
column8:
Discover hidden surprises under each of the 7 chunky wooden puzzle pieces. What is in the Barn? The only way to find out is to take out the pieces and put them in again and again. Matching pieces to appropriate shapes helps little ones learn shape and animal recognition.

Each puzzle develops fine motor skills, problem solving and imagination.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® All Aboard Alphabet Learning Train
column8:
This colorful train puzzle is over 3 feet long and includes 30 extra large pieces. All aboard as you join the exotic animals on the circus train that teaches the 26 letters of the alphabet.

Each puzzle develops alphabet recognition, fine motor skills and problem solving.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: Little People® ABC Puzzle Block Set
column8:
The Little People® ABC Puzzle Block Set includes 30 classic wood blocks, with four sides of play, that teach upper and lower case letters, basic shapes and beginner words. The blocks also fit together to form a challenging farm scene puzzle!

All the blocks store in the convenient tray for easy clean up.

For more information, please contact TCG at 1-877-212-3388.

column6: The Del Mar Convertible Crib with Just the Right Height™ Feature
Deluxe Wide Opening Diaper Bag with the FastFinder™ Pocket System (Brown)
column7: The Deluxe Wide Opening Diaper Bag features frame construction that opens extra wide…and stays open!
column8:
Featuring the FastFinder™ Pocket System, all of your key items are at arms’ reach on the exterior of the bag with easy-to-find labels. The insulated bottles pocket keeps bottles cold. The exterior wipes case can be accessed with a press of a button, so you can grab a wipe with one hand and hold onto baby with the other! The pacifier pocket can be easily wiped clean. And the diapers pocket is large enough for multiple changes. The labels also help secondary users locate and replace these essentials so they’re sure to be just where you left them…so you’ll have what you need – when baby needs it!

Features
•Frame construction opens extra wide and stays open.
•Nylon twill construction and printed nylon lining.
•Eight exterior pockets, including four FastFinder™ pockets for bottles, pacifiers, diapers, and wipes, and pockets for the changing pad, extras, and your personal items.
•One insulated zippered bottle pocket.
•Exterior wipes pocket includes wipes case that can be accessed without removing it from the bag.
•Six interior nylon pockets to help organize your everyday items like children’s cups, snacks, creams, and a change of clothes.
•Can be carried using the adjustable shoulder strap with padded strap cover, or easy-to-grab top handles with strap cover.
•Includes a cushioned changing pad and a baby wipe case.
•Four plastic feet to help keep the bottom of your bag clean.
•Dimensions (inches): 17 wide x 12 ½ tall x 6 deep.

Available exclusively at Babies "R" Us®.

For more information, please contact ADSutton at 1-800-695-8895.

column6: Deluxe Sporty Diaper Backpack with the FastFinder™ Pocket System (Brown)
column7: For the active parent about town, the Deluxe Sporty Diaper Backpack is the ultimate hands-free organization solution.
column8:
Featuring the FastFinder™ Pocket System, all of your key items are at arm’s reach on the exterior of the bag with easy-to-find labels. The insulated bottles pocket keeps bottles cold. The exterior wipes case can be accessed with a press of a button, so you can grab a wipe with one hand and hold onto baby with the other! The pacifier pocket can be easily wiped clean. column8:
Sometimes your little one likes being held over your shoulder. Sometimes on your knee. Other times, she wants to be cradled in your arms as you rock her side-to-side or back-and-forth. But for the times you need to put baby down, here’s a swing that cradles and swings, soothes and entertains her just the way she likes it! It surrounds her in plush, cozy fabrics and a canopy that cocoons her. The soothing continues with eight tunes and a side-to-side cradle motion, a lot like the way you rock her in your arms. When your little lamb is ready for play, the swinging changes to a back-and-forth motion (because babies love variety) and she’s engaged with nature sound tracks and a mobile featuring a mirror, floating clouds and little lambs to entertain her. Includes six soothing swing speeds, little plush friend tethered right to the removable tray, and bead bar. Sturdy steel frame has legs that fold in for storage and portability. Requires 4 D batteries.

Weight Limit: 25 lbs. (11.3 kg)

Developmental Guidelines: Use cradle swing from birth until a child becomes active and can climb out of the seat.
